class elsiana {

    String serial;
    String name_client ; 
    String name_elfne;
     String id ;
    String type_siana;
    String date;
    String id_elfne;
    String region ;
    double price ;
    public elsiana(String serial,
            String name_client ,
    
            String id,
           
            String type_siana,
            String date,
            String id_elfne,
            String name_elfne ,
              String region 
    ,double price) {
        this.serial = serial;
        this.id = id;
        
        this.type_siana = type_siana;
        this.date = date;
        this.id_elfne = id_elfne;
        this.region=region;
        this.name_client=name_client;
        this.name_elfne=name_elfne;
        this.price=price ;
    }
}

class elsiana_gdeda {

    String serial;
    String id;
    String date_regist;
     String dead_line;
    String date;
    String mark;
    String id_elfne;
    String id_elmndob;
    String name_elmndonb ;
    String region;
    String name_client;
    String name_elfne;
    String id_elmndob_elwaset;
    String name_elmndob_elwaset;
    double price  ;
    String what_done;
    public elsiana_gdeda(String serial,
            String name_client ,
            String id,
            String date_Regist ,
             String dead_line ,
            String date,
            String mark,
            String id_elfne,
            String name_elfne ,
            String id_elmndob , 
            String name_elmndob
            , String id_elmndob_elwaset
            , String name_elmndob_elwaset
    , String region ,double price ,String what_done) {
        this.serial = serial;
        this.id = id;
        this.date_regist=date_Regist;
        this.dead_line = dead_line;
         this.date = date;
        this.mark = mark;
        this.id_elmndob = id_elmndob;
        this.id_elfne = id_elfne;
       this.region=region;
       this.name_elmndonb=name_elmndob;
       this.name_client=name_client ;
       this.name_elmndob_elwaset=name_elmndob_elwaset ;
       this.id_elmndob_elwaset=id_elmndob_elwaset;
       this.name_elfne=name_elfne;
       this.price=price ;
       this.what_done=what_done;
    }
}

    String content_file_users = "";

    void load_users() {


        java.io.File f = new java.io.File(directory,"CUSTOMER_SERVICES_USERS.txt");
        String user = "";
        if (f.exists()) {
            Scanner s = null;
            try {
                s = new Scanner(f);
            } catch (FileNotFoundException ex) {
            }
            if(s.hasNext())
            {
                user = s.nextLine();
               content_file_users += user + "\n";
                jComboBox_users.addItem(user);
                 jTextField1.setText(jComboBox_users.getItemAt(0).toString());
            }
            while (s.hasNext()) {
                user = s.nextLine();
                content_file_users += user + "\n";
                jComboBox_users.addItem(user);
            }
         
        }
        System.out.println(content_file_users);
       
    }
void get_numbers(String name ,String text)
{
    jLabel_name_numbers.setText(name);
    model_numbers.setRowCount(0);
    String t="";
    for (int i=0 ; i<text.length() ; i++)
    { 
       if ((int)text.charAt(i)>47&&(int)text.charAt(i)<58)
       {
           t+=text.charAt(i);
       }
       else
       {
           if (text.charAt(i)=='-')
           {
               model_numbers.addRow(new Object[]{t});
               t="";
           }
       }
    }
    model_numbers.addRow(new Object[]{t});
}
    void add_user_history(String user) {
        here:
        {
            for ( int i=0 ; i<jComboBox_users.getItemCount() ; i++)
            {
                    if (user.equals(String.valueOf(jComboBox_users.getItemAt(i)))) {
                        break here;
                    }
                
            }
             java.io.File f = new java.io.File(directory,"CUSTOMER_SERVICES_USERS.txt");
            
            PrintWriter w;
            try {
                w = new PrintWriter(f);

                w.println(user);
                w.print(content_file_users);
                w.close();
            } catch (FileNotFoundException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
          
        }
    }

    void login(String enable) {
        String time_now = m.ob.time_now();

                  
                   
                  
                    try { 
//                    bk.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
//                    ResultSet rs_mon_rest = bk.stmt.executeQuery("select* from information_hr");
//                      if (rs_mon_rest.next())  
//                    {   enable = rs_mon_rest.getString("enable");}
                        ////////////////////////////// class /////////////////////////////////////
                      
                        if (!enable.equals("0")) {
                          
                           
                           

                            

                                {
                                    String start_auto = "";
                                   
                                   bk.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                                    ResultSet rs_auto = bk.stmt.executeQuery(
                                            "select c.serial , c.date_remake_class , c.num_month_remake_class , c.class , c.elmosthdaf ,(select count(s.serial) from elsiana s where c.serial= s.serial  and s.date between DATE_SUB(c.date_remake_class, INTERVAL 1 year) and c.date_remake_class )as counter from clients_product c where c.date_remake_class < now() and class<>'-'"
                                            //" select c.id_client , c.id_product , c.date_buy , c.date_remake_class , c.num_month_remake_class , c.class , c.elmosthdaf , count(s.id_client) from clients_product c left join elsiana s on c.id_client= s.id_client and c.id_product=s.id_product and c.date_buy=s.date_buy and s.date between DATE_SUB(c.date_remake_class, INTERVAL 1 year) and c.date_remake_class where c.date_remake_class < now()  and class<>'-' group by s.id_client , s.id_product , s.date_buy");
                                    );
                                            while (rs_auto.next()) {
                                        bk.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                                        int counter = rs_auto.getInt("counter");
                                        String serial = rs_auto.getString("serial");
                                       
                                        String date_remake_class = rs_auto.getString("date_remake_class");
                                        String num_month_remake_class = rs_auto.getString("num_month_remake_class");
                                        String old_class=rs_auto.getString("class");
                                        int elmosthdaf = rs_auto.getInt("elmosthdaf");
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                        int i=0 ;
                                        for (; i<class_list.size() ; i++)
                                        {
                                            if (counter * 100 / elmosthdaf >=class_list.get(i).percent)
                                            {
                                                break ;
                                            }
                                        }
                                         bk.stmt.executeUpdate("update clients_product set class='"+class_list.get(i).class_+"'  , date_remake_class='" + m.ob.time_month(date_remake_class,
                                                    Integer.parseInt(num_month_remake_class)) + "' where serial=" + serial
                                                 );
                                        bk.stmt.executeUpdate("insert into client_class_history values ("
                                                +"default"+",'"+serial+"','"+old_class+"','"+class_list.get(i).class_+"','"+counter
                                                +"','"+time_now+"')");
                                         JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "?? ?????? ?????? ???? ????? "+serial+" ? ???? ?? ????? "
                                                 +old_class+" ??? ????? "+class_list.get(i).class_+" ??????? "+counter+" ?????? ?? ?????? "+elmosthdaf);
////////////////////////////
                                    }
                                }

                           


                        }

                    } catch (SQLException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                 
    }

                        } catch (FileNotFoundException ex) {
                            JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "???? ?? ??? ????? ??? ??????");
                        }
                        if (s.hasNext()) {
                            admin_user = s.nextLine();
                            admin_pass = s.nextLine();
                            ip = s.nextLine();

                        }
                        s.close();

//                            public void run()
//                            {
//                                login();
//                            }}.start();
//                 
                              m.add_client.set_action_pansels("T");
                              
                              
                            add_user_history(jTextField1.getText());
                            jPasswordField1.setFocusable(false);
                            m.animation(jPanel_login, m.height);
                           
                           
                           
                            get_classes();
                           
                            user_name = jTextField1.getText();
                            password = jPasswordField1.getText();
                            m.jLabel_current_user.setText(user_name);
                             bk=new Get_backup(this) {}  ;
                             new Thread(bk).start();
                             alarm_damage();
                             alarm_siana_gdeda();
                             alarm_trkeb();
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns("installation_table.txt",m.jTable_trkeb);
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns_customer_service();
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns( "company_rep_siana.txt" ,jTable_clients_siana);
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns( "company_rep_el3otl.txt" ,jTable_clients_el23tal);
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns( "company_rep_trkeb.txt" ,jTable_fatorh_elsiana2);
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns( "company_rep_siana_gdeda.txt" ,jTable_fatorh_elsiana3);
                            sort_table.reload_sorted_columns( "company_rep_el2st.txt" , jTable_co_el2st);
                       
                             //  th_ob.start();
                        setLocation(x_screen,y_screen);
                       setSize(1230, 725);
                      
                        } else {
                         JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "???? ?? ????? ?? ????? ???????? ???? ???? ???? ???? ????? ? ???? ?????? ?? ????? ????????");

                        }
  
                      
                       
                    

                } catch (ClassNotFoundException ex) {
                    ex.printStackTrace();

                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "error \n check your connection with server");
                   
                   

                } catch (SQLException ex) {
                    ex.printStackTrace();
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "error \n check your connection with server");
                     
                   
                }
            }
            
        }
     

    }
    //////////////////////////////////////////// classes ///////////////////////////////////////////////////
    class classes{
        String class_ ;
        double percent ;
        String p1 ;String p2 ;String p3 ;String p5 ;String p6 ;String p7 ;
        public classes(String class_ , double percent , String p1 ,String p2 ,String p3 ,String p5 ,String p6 ,String p7 ) {
            this.class_=class_;
            this.percent=percent;
            this.p1=p1 ;
            this.p2=p2 ;
            this.p3=p3 ;
            this.p5=p5 ;
            this.p6=p6 ;
            this.p7=p7 ;
        }
        
    }
    boolean check_class_filter(String key)
    {
        for (int i=0 ; i<class_filter_list.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (key.equals(class_filter_list.get(i)))
            {
                return true ;
            }
        }
     return false ;
    }
    List<classes> class_list=new ArrayList<>();
    List <String> class_filter_list=new ArrayList<>();
    List<JCheckBox> classes_checkbox=new ArrayList<>();
     JCheckBox  box ;
    void get_classes()
    {
       class_list.clear();
        m.jComboBox_class_add_client.removeAllItems();m.jPanel_classes.removeAll();
        try {
            m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs=m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select * from classes order by percent desc");
            while(rs.next())
            {
               class_list.add(new classes(rs.getString(1),rs.getDouble(2),rs.getString(3),rs.getString(4),rs.getString(5),rs.getString(6)
               ,rs.getString(7),rs.getString(8)));
               jComboBox_class_clients_report.addItem(rs.getString(1));
               m.jComboBox_class_add_client.addItem(rs.getString(1));
               
               class_filter_list.add(rs.getString(1));
               box=new JCheckBox(rs.getString(1));  
                box.setForeground(new Color(72,72,72));
                box.setFont(m.font.deriveFont(13f));
                box.setComponentOrientation(ComponentOrientation.RIGHT_TO_LEFT);
                box.setSelected(true);
                box.setBounds(5, class_list.size()*30, 140, 25);
                classes_checkbox.add(box);
                box.addActionListener(new ActionListener() {
            public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
                class_filter_list.clear();
               for (int i=0 ; i<classes_checkbox.size() ; i++)
               {
                   if (classes_checkbox.get(i).isSelected())
                   {
                       class_filter_list.add(classes_checkbox.get(i).getLabel());
                   }
               }
               m.elsiana.search();
            }
        });
               m.jPanel_classes.add(box);
              // m.jComboBox_class_elsiana.addItem(rs.getString(1));
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }
    void search_client_com2(String key) {
    }

    void add(int i) {
        String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));

        String name_client = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 1));

        String date1 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 9));
        String date2 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 10));
        String date3 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 11));
        String date5 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 12));
        String date6 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 13));
        String date7 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 14));
        String region_s = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 2));


        String id_client = "";
        String id_product = "";
        String date_buy = "";


        String region = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 2));
        String phone = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 3));
        String hints = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 4));
        String rsed_1 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 29));
        String rsed_2 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 30));
        String rsed_3 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 31));
        String rsed_5 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 32));
        String rsed_6 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 33));
        String rsed_7 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 34));

        // if (flag_siana_or_part == false) {
        // x = jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        id_client = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 0));
        id_product = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 5));
        date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
        String name_product = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 6));
        String quantitty = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 7));
        String siana_1 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 23));
        String siana_2 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 24));
        String siana_3 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 25));
        String siana_5 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 26));
        String siana_6 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 27));
        String siana_7 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 28));
        String type_3otl = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 16));
        String date_wrong = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 17));
        String date_end = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 19));
        String wrongs = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 16));
        String nezam_eldf3 = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 18));
        String el2st_product = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 20));
        String date_el2st = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 21));
        String elb2e = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 22));
        String quantity = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 7));
        String siana_elb2e = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 35));

        String elmosthdaf = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 37));
        String date_remake_class = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 38));
        String num_month_remake_class = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 39));
        String type_siana = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 15));
        
        String home_num = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 40));
        String street = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 41));
        String country = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 42));
         model_search_client.addRow(new Object[]{id_client, name_client, region, phone, hints, id_product, name_product, quantity, date_buy, date1, date2, date3, date5, date6, date7, "",
                            wrongs, date_wrong, nezam_eldf3, date_end, el2st_product,
                            date_el2st, elb2e, siana_1, siana_2, siana_3, siana_5, siana_6, siana_7, rsed_1, rsed_2, rsed_3, rsed_5, rsed_6
                 , rsed_7, siana_elb2e, clas, elmosthdaf, date_remake_class, num_month_remake_class, home_num, street, country
         ,String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 43))});

    }

    void search() {
        String key = jTextField_n_p.getText();
        String key_end = ((JTextField) jTextField_en.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        String key_start = ((JTextField) jTextField_st.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        model_search_client.setRowCount(0);


        if (jComboBox_class_clients_report.getSelectedIndex() == 0) {

            if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 0) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String name_client = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 1));

                    if (name_client.contains(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }

            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 1) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {





                    String name_product = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 6));

                    if (name_product.startsWith(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }
                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 2) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {



                    String region_s = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 2));



                    if (region_s.startsWith(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }
                }

            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 3) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        if (m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }
                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 4) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String country = "";
                    country = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 42));

                    if (country.startsWith(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 5) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String country = "";
                    country = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 42));
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        if (country.startsWith(key) && m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                }
            }
              else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex()==6) {

            for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {

                 
                String hints = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 4));

                if (hints.contains(key)) {
                    
                    
                         add(i);
                }

            }



        }

             else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex()==7) {

            for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {

                 
                String hints = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 4));

                if (!hints.contains(key)) {
                    
                    
                         add(i);
                }

            }



        }
             else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 8) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                   
                    String region = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 2));
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        if (region.startsWith(key) && m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                }
            }
else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 9) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                     
                  String  street = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 41));

                    if (street.contains(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 10) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    
                   String street = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 41));
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        if (street.contains(key) && m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                }
            }
            else  if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 11) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String column_content = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, jTable_siana.getSelectedColumn()));

                    if (column_content.contains(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }

            }
        }       else {
            String clas_comp =  String.valueOf(jComboBox_class_clients_report.getSelectedItem());
            System.out.println(clas_comp);
            if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 0) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String name_client = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 1));
                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    if (name_client.contains(key) && clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }

            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 1) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {


                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));


                    String name_product = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 6));

                    if (name_product.startsWith(key) && clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp)) {
                        add(i);
                    }
                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 2) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {



                    String region_s = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 2));
                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));


                    if (region_s.startsWith(key) && clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp)) {
                        add(i);
                    }
                }

            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 3) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));

                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    if (date_buy.equals(key) && clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp)) {
                        add(i);
                    }
                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 4) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String country = "";
                    country = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 42));
                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp) && country.startsWith(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 5) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String country = "";
                    country = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 42));
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                        if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp) && country.startsWith(key) && m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                }
            }

  else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex()==6) {

            for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {

                 
                String hints = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 4));
 String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp) &&hints.contains(key)) {
                    
                    
                         add(i);
                }

            }



        }

             else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex()==7) {

            for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {

                 
                String hints = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 4));
 String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp)&&!hints.contains(key)) {
                    
                    
                         add(i);
                }

            }



        }

            else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 8) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                   
                    String region = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 2));
                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp) &&region.startsWith(key) && m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                }
            }
else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 9) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                     
                  String  street = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 41));
String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp) &&street.contains(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }
            } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 10) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                   String street = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 41));
                    String date_buy = "";
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 8));
                    try {
                        if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp) &&street.contains(key) && m.ob.time_between(key_start, date_buy, key_end)) {
                            add(i);
                        }
                    } catch (ParseException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }

                }
            }
                 else  if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 11) {

                for (int i = 0; i < m.model_siana_help.getRowCount(); i++) {
                    String column_content = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, jTable_siana.getSelectedColumn()));
 String clas = String.valueOf(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase(clas_comp)&&column_content.contains(key)) {
                        add(i);
                    }

                }

            }
        }
        jLabel_count.setText(String.valueOf(model_search_client.getRowCount()));
    }int get_client_from_back_table(String serial )
{
    for (int i=0 ; i<m.model_siana_help.getRowCount() ; i++)
    {
        if (serial.equals(m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 43)))
        {
            return i ;
        }
       
    } 
    return -1 ;
}

   List <String> regions_rep=new ArrayList<>();
 
    void rep1() {
        try {
            regions_rep.clear();
            model_elkta3_info.setRowCount(0);
            model_elkta3_info_country.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select country from elkta3_dependant where id_elkta3= "
                    + String.valueOf(model_elkta3.getValueAt(jTable_main_elkta3.getSelectedRow(), 0)));
            while (rs.next()) {
                String country = rs.getString("country");
                model_elkta3_info_country.addRow(new Object[]{country});

                m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                ResultSet rs_regions = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select region from countries where country= '"
                        + country + "'");
                while (rs_regions.next()) {
                    model_elkta3_info.addRow(new Object[]{rs_regions.getString(1)});
                    regions_rep.add(rs_regions.getString(1));
                }
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }

    }

    void rep2() {

        clear_varibles();
        //////////////////// elsiana filter ///////////////
        
        model_clients_sianat.setRowCount(0);
        for (int i = 0; i < elsiana_list_Done.size(); i++) {
          
                

                for (int w = 0; w < model_elkta3_info.getRowCount(); w++) {
                    try{
                    if (elsiana_list_Done.get(i).region.equals(model_elkta3_info.getValueAt(w, 0))) {
                       
    model_clients_sianat.addRow(new Object[]{elsiana_list_Done.get(i).serial, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).name_client,elsiana_list_Done.get(i).id,
       elsiana_list_Done.get(i).type_siana, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).date, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).id_elfne,elsiana_list_Done.get(i).name_elfne,
        elsiana_list_Done.get(i).region,elsiana_list_Done.get(i).price});
           total_elsiana+=elsiana_list_Done.get(i).price;
                      break;
                    }
                    }catch (Exception e){}
                }
           
        } 
      //  int c_0 = 0 ;
        for (int i = 0; i < elsiana_list_not_Done.size(); i++) {
           

                for (int w = 0; w < model_elkta3_info.getRowCount(); w++) {

             arr_elsiana[0]++ ;
                      break;
                    }
 }catch (Exception e){}
                }

    void client_report() {
        try {
           
                    model_search_client.setRowCount(0);
            m.model_siana_help.setRowCount(0);

          ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery(  " select * from clients_product cs left outer join clients c on cs.id_client=c.id_client left"
                                + " outer join product p on p.id_product=cs.id_product left outer join countries co on co.region=cs.region "
                               + " order by cs.id_client                 "
          );
            while (rs.next()) {
                //  try {
                String id_client = String.valueOf(rs.getString("id_client"));
                String id_product = String.valueOf(rs.getString("id_product"));
                String quantity = String.valueOf(rs.getString("quantity"));
                String hints = rs.getString("hints");
                String date_buy = rs.getString("date_buy");
                String date1 = rs.getString("date1");
                String date2 = rs.getString("date2");
                String date3 = rs.getString("date3");
                //joptionpane.showMessageDialog(null, id_client);
                String date5 = rs.getString("date5");
                String date6 = rs.getString("date6");
                String date7 = rs.getString("date7");
                String siana_1 = rs.getString("siana_1");
                String siana_2 = rs.getString("siana_2");
                String siana_3 = rs.getString("siana_3");
                String siana_5 = rs.getString("siana_5");
                String siana_6 = rs.getString("siana_6");
                String siana_7 = rs.getString("siana_7");
                String rsed_1 = rs.getString("rsed1");
                String rsed_2 = rs.getString("rsed2");
                String rsed_3 = rs.getString("rsed3");
                String rsed_5 = rs.getString("rsed5");
                String rsed_6 = rs.getString("rsed6");
                String rsed_7 = rs.getString("rsed7");
                String nezam_eldf3 = String.valueOf(rs.getString("nezam_eldf3"));
                String date_el2st = rs.getString("date_el2st");
                String elb2e = String.valueOf(rs.getString("elb2e"));
                String region = rs.getString("region");
                String home_num = rs.getString("home_num");
                String street = rs.getString("street");

//                            String wrongs = rs.getString("wrongs");
//                            String date_wrong = rs.getString("date_wrong");
//                            String date_end = rs.getString("date_end_line_el3otl");
                String siana_elb2e = rs.getString("total_elb2e_sian");
                String clas = rs.getString("class");
                String elmosthdaf = rs.getString("elmosthdaf");
                String num_month_remake_class = rs.getString("num_month_remake_class");
                String date_remake_class = rs.getString("date_remake_class");
                String wrongs = "";
                String date_wrong = "";
                String date_end = "";
//                m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
//                ResultSet rs_el3otl = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select wrong , date , dead_line from wrongs "
//                        + " where id_client=" + id_client + " and id_product=" + id_product + " and date_buy='" + date_buy + "'");
//
//                while (rs_el3otl.next())
//                {
//
//                    wrongs = rs.getString("wrong");
//                    date_wrong = rs.getString("date");
//                    date_end = rs.getString("dead_line");
//                }



//                Statement stmt2 = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
//                ResultSet rs2 = stmt2.executeQuery("select name_client  , phone from clients where id_client =" + id_client);
//                rs2.next();
                String name_client = rs.getString("name_client");

                String phone = String.valueOf(rs.getString("phone"));


//                Statement stmt3 = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
//                ResultSet rs3 = stmt3.executeQuery("select name_product, el2st from product where id_product =" + id_product);
                String name_product = "";
                String el2st_product = "";
              //  if (rs3.next())
                {
                    name_product = rs.getString("name_product");
                    el2st_product = rs.getString("el2st");
                }
              String serial=rs.getString("serial");

                //joptionpane.showMessageDialog(null, date5);

                String country = rs.getString("country");//m.ob.c(region);
                model_search_client.addRow(new Object[]{id_client, name_client, region, phone, hints, id_product, name_product, quantity, date_buy, date1, date2, date3, date5, date6, date7, "",
                            wrongs, date_wrong, nezam_eldf3, date_end, el2st_product,
                            date_el2st, elb2e, siana_1, siana_2, siana_3, siana_5, siana_6, siana_7, rsed_1, rsed_2, rsed_3, rsed_5, rsed_6, rsed_7, siana_elb2e, 
                            clas, elmosthdaf, date_remake_class, num_month_remake_class, home_num, street, country,serial});
                m.model_siana_help.addRow(new Object[]{id_client, name_client, region, phone, hints, id_product, name_product, quantity, date_buy, date1, date2, date3, date5, date6, date7, "",
                            wrongs, date_wrong, nezam_eldf3, date_end, el2st_product,
                            date_el2st, elb2e, siana_1, siana_2, siana_3, siana_5, siana_6, siana_7, rsed_1, rsed_2, rsed_3, rsed_5, rsed_6, rsed_7, siana_elb2e,
                            clas, elmosthdaf, date_remake_class, num_month_remake_class, home_num, street, country,serial});
            }
            rs.close();
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
        
        jLabel_count.setText(String.valueOf(model_search_client.getRowCount()));
        //  JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(rootPane,String.valueOf(model_search_client.getRowCount()) );
    }
    private void jTextField_search_elkta3KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_search_elkta3KeyReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:
        try {
            model_elkta3_insert.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select * from elkta3 where name_elkta3 like '" + jTextField_search_elkta3.getText() + "%'");
            while (rs.next()) {
                model_elkta3_insert.addRow(new Object[]{
                            rs.getString("id_elkta3"),
                            rs.getString("name_elkta3"),
                            rs.getString("date_construct"),
                            rs.getString("name_manager")
                        });
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_search_elkta3KeyReleased

    private void jTable_elkt3atKeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elkt3atKeyReleased
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_elkt3atKeyReleased

    private void jTextField_search_regionKeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_search_regionKeyReleased
        String key = jTextField_search_region.getText();
        model_elkta3_regions.setRowCount(0);
        for (int i = 0; i < regions_elkta3.size(); i++) {
            String rec = regions_elkta3.get(i);
            if (rec.startsWith(key)) {
                model_elkta3_regions.addRow(new Object[]{rec});
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_search_regionKeyReleased

    private void jTextField_search_all_regionsKeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_search_all_regionsKeyReleased
        String key = jTextField_search_all_regions.getText();
        model_all_regions.setRowCount(0);
        for (int i = 0; i < regions_loaded.size(); i++) {
            String rec = regions_loaded.get(i);
            if (rec.startsWith(key)) {
                model_all_regions.addRow(new Object[]{rec});
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_search_all_regionsKeyReleased

    private void jTable_elkt3atMouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elkt3atMouseReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:
        try {
            // TODO add your handling code here:
            model_elkta3_regions.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            regions_elkta3.clear();
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select country from elkta3_dependant where id_elkta3= "
                    + String.valueOf(model_elkta3_insert.getValueAt(jTable_elkt3at.getSelectedRow(), 0)));
            System.out.println("select country from elkta3_dependant where id_elkta3= "
                    + String.valueOf(model_elkta3_insert.getValueAt(jTable_elkt3at.getSelectedRow(), 0)));
            while (rs.next()) {
                String re = rs.getString("country");
                model_elkta3_regions.addRow(new Object[]{
                            re
                        });
                regions_elkta3.add(re);
                System.out.println(model_elkta3_regions.getValueAt(0, 0));
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_elkt3atMouseReleased

    private void jTextField_NAME_elmndob_elmndob3KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_NAME_elmndob_elmndob3KeyReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:
        String key = jTextField_NAME_elmndob_elmndob.getText();
        model_elmndob_elmndob.setRowCount(0);
        try {
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.search_elmndob(key);

            while (rs.next()) {

                String id_elmndob = String.valueOf(rs.getString("id_elmndob"));
                String name_elmndob = rs.getString("name_elmndob");
                String phone = String.valueOf(rs.getString("phone"));
                model_elmndob_elmndob.addRow(new Object[]{id_elmndob, name_elmndob, phone});

            }

        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_NAME_elmndob_elmndob3KeyReleased

    private void jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE3KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE3KeyReleased
        /////TODO add your handling code here:
        String key = jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE.getText();
        model_elfne_ELFNE.setRowCount(0);

        ResultSet rs = null;
        try {
            rs = m.ob.search_elfne(key);
            while (rs.next()) {
                String id_elfne = String.valueOf(rs.getString("id_elfne"));

                String name_elfne = rs.getString("name_elfne");
                System.out.println("1");
                String phone = String.valueOf(rs.getString("phone"));
                String places = rs.getString("places");
                model_elfne_ELFNE.addRow(new Object[]{id_elfne, name_elfne, phone, places});

            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE3KeyReleased

    private void jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOBMouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOBMouseReleased

        int counter_m = 0;
        int counter_m_w = 0;

        int x = jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOB.getSelectedRow();

        String month_year_day_start = ((JTextField) jTextField_month_elmndob.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        String month_year_day_end = ((JTextField) jTextField_year_elmndob1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        try {
            if (x != -1 && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_start) == true && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_end) == true) {
                model_operations_elmndob.setRowCount(0);

                //  String time = m.ob.time_now();


                String id_elmndob = (String) model_elmndob_elmndob.getValueAt(x, 0);
m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select eltrkebat.* , clients.name_client , clients_product.quantity  , elmndob_elwaset.name_elmndob_elwaset "
        + "     from eltrkebat"
                        + " left join clients_product   "
                        + "on eltrkebat.serial=clients_product.serial "
                        + " left join clients on clients_product.id_client=clients.id_client  "
                        + " left join elmndob_elwaset on eltrkebat.id_elmndob_elwaset = elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset"
                        + " where eltrkebat.id_elmndob=" + id_elmndob
                        + " and eltrkebat.date between '" + month_year_day_start
                        + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");

                while (rs.next()) {

                    String serial = rs.getString("serial");
                     String id = rs.getString("id");
                    String id_elfne = rs.getString("id_elfne");
                    String id_elmndob_elwaset = rs.getString("id_elmndob_elwaset");
                    String mark = rs.getString("mark");
                   String   name_elmndob_elwaset = rs.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset");
                   String name_client = rs.getString("name_client");
                   String quantity = rs.getString("quantity");
                    
                  
                    if (id_elmndob_elwaset==null) {
                        counter_m++;
                    } else {
                        counter_m_w++;
                    }
                
                     
                  
                    model_operations_elmndob.addRow(new Object[]
                    {id,serial, name_client,  quantity, id_elfne, id_elmndob, id_elmndob_elwaset, name_elmndob_elwaset, mark,"?????"});
                }
                jLabel_mndob_m.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m));
                jLabel_mndob_m_w.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m_w));
//////////////////////////////////// siana gdeda ////////////////////////////////////////////////
                
                 counter_m = 0;
                  counter_m_w = 0;
        
                m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
  ResultSet rs_siana_gdeda = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select siana_gdeda_archive.* , clients.name_client , clients_product.quantity  , elmndob_elwaset.name_elmndob_elwaset "
        + "     from siana_gdeda_archive"
                        + " left join clients_product  "
                        + "on siana_gdeda_archive.serial=clients_product.serial "
                        + " left join clients on clients_product.id_client=clients.id_client  "
                        + " left join elmndob_elwaset on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob_elwaset = elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset"
                        + " where siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob=" + id_elmndob
                        + " and siana_gdeda_archive.date between '" + month_year_day_start
                        + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");

                while (rs_siana_gdeda.next()) {

                    String serial = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("serial");
                     String id = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id");
                    String id_elfne = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id_elfne");
                    String id_elmndob_elwaset = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id_elmndob_elwaset");
                    String mark = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("mark");
                   String   name_elmndob_elwaset = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset");
                   String name_client = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("name_client");
                   String quantity = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("quantity");
                    
                  
                    if (id_elmndob_elwaset==null) {
                        counter_m++;
                    } else {
                        counter_m_w++;
                    }
                
                     
                  
                    model_operations_elmndob.addRow(new Object[]
                    {id,serial, name_client,  quantity, id_elfne, id_elmndob, id_elmndob_elwaset, name_elmndob_elwaset, mark,"????? ?????"});
                }

                
               jLabel_mndob_m1.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m));
                jLabel_mndob_m_w1.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m_w));
                
                ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// canceled report //////////////////////////////////////////
                
                 int counter_canceled_trkeb = 0;
                 int counter_canceled_siana_gdeda = 0;
        model_elmndob_canceled.setRowCount(0);
                m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
  ResultSet rs_canceld = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select canceled_table.*    , elmndob_elwaset.name_elmndob_elwaset "
        + "     from canceled_table"
                        
                        + " left join elmndob_elwaset on canceled_table.id_elmndob_elwaset = elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset"
                        + " where canceled_table.id_elmndob=" + id_elmndob
                        + " and canceled_table.date between '" + month_year_day_start
                        + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");

                while (rs_canceld.next()) {

               if (rs_canceld.getString(9).equals("?????"))   counter_canceled_trkeb++ ;
               else if (rs_canceld.getString(9).equals("????? ?????"))counter_canceled_siana_gdeda++ ;
                   
                  model_elmndob_canceled.addRow(new Object[]
                    {rs_canceld.getString(1),rs_canceld.getString(2),rs_canceld.getString(3),rs_canceld.getString(4),
                  rs_canceld.getString(5),rs_canceld.getString(6),rs_canceld.getString(9),rs_canceld.getString(7),
                  rs_canceld.getString(8),rs_canceld.getString(10)});
                }

           jLabel_mndob_trkebat_rejects.setText(String.valueOf(counter_canceled_trkeb));
             jLabel_mndob_trkebat_rejects1.setText(String.valueOf(counter_canceled_siana_gdeda));
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
           Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        } 
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOBMouseReleased

    private void jTable_elfne_ELFNEMouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elfne_ELFNEMouseReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:

        double total = 0;
        int counter = 0;
       double price_elsiana=0 ,price_el3otl=0 ,price_eltrkeb=0 ,price_siana_gdeda=0 ;
//        double price_siana = 0;
//        double price_3otl = 0;
//        double price_trkeb = 0;

        int num_siana = 0;
        int num_3otl = 0;
        int num_trkeb = 0;
        int num_siana_gdeda =0 ;
        String month_year_day_start = ((JTextField) jTextField_month_ELFNE.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();

        String month_year_day_end = ((JTextField) jTextField_year_ELFNE1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        int counter_places = 0;
        int x = jTable_elfne_ELFNE.getSelectedRow();
        //   String month = jTextField_month_ELFNE.getText();
      
            if (x != -1 && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_end) == true && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_start) == true) {
                model_operations_ELFNE.setRowCount(0);

                String time = m.ob.time_now();
                //            String year = jTextField_year_ELFNE1.getText();
                //
                //            System.out.println(year);
                //             = year + "-" + month + "-01";
                //
                //             = "";
                //            try {
                //                month_year_day_end = m.ob.time(month_year_day_start, 31);
                //            } catch (ParseException ex) {
                //                Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                //            }

                String id_elfne = (String) model_elfne_ELFNE.getValueAt(x, 0);
                try {
                    ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select elsiana.* , clients.name_client from elsiana "
                            + " left join clients_product on elsiana.serial=clients_product.serial "
                            + "  left join clients on clients.id_client=clients_product.id_client "
                            + "where"
                            + " elsiana.id_elfne=" + id_elfne + " and elsiana.date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");
                   

                    while (rs.next()) {
                   
                        counter++;
                        num_siana++;
                        String serial = rs.getString("serial");
                        String id = rs.getString("id");
                        String type_elsiana = rs.getString("type_elsiana");
                        String date = rs.getString("date");
                        String name_client= rs.getString("name_client");
                        double price=rs.getDouble("price");
                        price_elsiana+=price ;
                        model_operations_ELFNE.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial,name_client, type_elsiana + "????? -", date,price});


                    }



                    String places_elfne = String.valueOf(model_elfne_ELFNE.getValueAt(x, 3));
//                    m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
//                    ResultSet rs_places = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select country , num_clients from num_operation"
//                            + ""
//                            + " where date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");
//
//                    while (rs_places.next()) {
//                        String region = rs_places.getString("country");
//
//                   
//                        if (places_elfne.contains(region)) {
//                            String num_clients = rs_places.getString("num_clients");
//                            counter_places += Double.parseDouble(num_clients);
//                        }
//                    }
                String Real_places_elfne="'";
                String curr="";
                for (int i=0 ; i<places_elfne.length() ; i++)
                {
                    if(places_elfne.charAt(i)=='#')
                    {
                        Real_places_elfne+=curr+"','";
                        curr="";
                    }else
                    {
                        curr+=places_elfne.charAt(i);
                    }
                }
                Real_places_elfne+=curr+"'";
                    System.out.println(Real_places_elfne);
                    m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                    ResultSet rs_places = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery(
//                            "select sum(num_clients)  from num_operation"
//                            
//                            + " where date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "' and region in "
//                            + "( select region from countries where country in ("+Real_places_elfne+"))"
                          "select (select count(*) from clients_product where( date1 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+
                                  "'"+" or date2 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date3 between "+"'"
                                  +month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date5 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+
                                  month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date6 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date7"
                                  + " between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" ) and class <> '-' and region in (select"
                                  + " region from countries where country  in ("+Real_places_elfne+" )) ) "
                    + "+"+"(select count(*) from elsiana s left join clients_product cs on  s.serial=cs.serial "
                                  + " where date between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" and "
                                  + "cs.region in (select region from countries where country  in ("+Real_places_elfne+" )) ) as sum"
                    );
                    System.out.println("select (select count(*) from clients_product where( date1 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+
                                  "'"+" or date2 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date3 between "+"'"
                                  +month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date5 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+
                                  month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date6 between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" or date7"
                                  + " between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" ) and class <> '-' and region in (select"
                                  + " region from countries where country  in ("+Real_places_elfne+" )) ) "
                    + "+"+"(select count(*) from elsiana s left join clients_product cs on  s.serial=cs.serial "
                                  + " where date between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" and "
                                  + "cs.region in (select region from countries where country  in ("+Real_places_elfne+" )) ) as sum");
                    if (rs_places.next())
                    {
                        counter_places=rs_places.getInt(1);
                    }
                    
                    
                    m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();

                    ResultSet rs_el3otl_num = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select el3otl.* , clients.name_client from el3otl "
                               + " left join clients_product on el3otl.serial=clients_product.serial "
                            + "  left join clients on clients.id_client=clients_product.id_client "
                            + " where el3otl.id_elfne=" + id_elfne + " and  el3otl.date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");

                    while (rs_el3otl_num.next()) {
                        num_3otl++;
                        counter++;
                        String serial  = rs_el3otl_num.getString("serial");
                        String id  = rs_el3otl_num.getString("id");
                        String type_elsiana = rs_el3otl_num.getString("type_el3otl");
                        String date = rs_el3otl_num.getString("date");
                        String mark = rs_el3otl_num.getString("mark");
                         String name_client= rs_el3otl_num.getString("name_client");
                        double price=rs_el3otl_num.getDouble("price");
                        price_el3otl+=price ;
                        model_operations_ELFNE.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial,name_client,  type_elsiana + "??? -" + " -" + mark, date,price});

                    }





                    m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                    ResultSet rs_trkebat = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select eltrkebat.* , clients.name_client from eltrkebat "
                              + " left join clients_product on eltrkebat.serial=clients_product.serial "
                            + "  left join clients on clients.id_client=clients_product.id_client "
                            + " where eltrkebat.id_elfne=" + id_elfne + " and  eltrkebat.date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");


                    while (rs_trkebat.next()) {
                        String serial = rs_trkebat.getString("serial");
                      String id = rs_trkebat.getString("id");
                        String date = rs_trkebat.getString("date");

                        String id_elmndob = rs_trkebat.getString("id_elmndob");
                        String name_client= rs_trkebat.getString("name_client");
                        counter++;
                        num_trkeb++;
                        double price=rs_trkebat.getDouble("price");
                        price_eltrkeb+=price ;
                        model_operations_ELFNE.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial,name_client,  "?????" , date,price});
                    }
                     m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                    ResultSet rs_siana_gdeda = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select siana_gdeda_archive.* , clients.name_client from siana_gdeda_archive "
                               + " left join clients_product on siana_gdeda_archive.serial=clients_product.serial "
                            + "  left join clients on clients.id_client=clients_product.id_client "
                            + " where siana_gdeda_archive.id_elfne=" + id_elfne + " and  siana_gdeda_archive.date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");


                    while (rs_siana_gdeda.next()) {
                        String serial = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("serial");
                        String id = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id");
                       
                        String date = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("date");

                        String id_elmndob = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id_elmndob");
                        String name_client= rs_siana_gdeda.getString("name_client");
                        counter++;
                        num_siana_gdeda++;
                        double price=rs_siana_gdeda.getDouble("price");
                        price_siana_gdeda+=price;
                        model_operations_ELFNE.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial,name_client,  "????? ?????" , date,price});
                    }



                } catch (SQLException ex) {
                    Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                }
               

                
                jLabel_TOTAL_PRICE1.setText(String.valueOf(counter));
                
                jLabel_TOTAL_PRICE2.setText(String.valueOf(counter_places));

                


                jLabel_elfne_num_siana.setText(String.valueOf(price_elsiana)+"/"+String.valueOf(num_siana));
                jLabel_elfne_num_el23tal.setText(String.valueOf(price_el3otl)+"/"+String.valueOf(num_3otl));
                jLabel_elfne_num_trkebat.setText(String.valueOf(price_eltrkeb)+"/"+String.valueOf(num_trkeb));
                jLabel_elfne_num_siana_gdeda.setText(String.valueOf(price_siana_gdeda)+"/"+String.valueOf(num_siana_gdeda));








            }

        try {
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.search_elmndob_elwaset(key);

            while (rs.next()) {

                String id_elmndob = String.valueOf(rs.getString("id_elmndob_elwaset"));

    private void jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOB1MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOB1MouseReleased
        int counter_m_w = 0;
        int counter_m_w_m = 0;

        int x = jTable_elMNDOB_ELMNDOB1.getSelectedRow();

        String month_year_day_start = ((JTextField) jTextField_month_elmndob1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        String month_year_day_end = ((JTextField) jTextField_year_elmndob2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        try {
            if (x != -1 && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_start) == true && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_end) == true) {
                model_operations_elmndob_elwset.setRowCount(0);

                String time = m.ob.time_now();


                String id_elmndob_elwaset = (String) model_elmndob_elmndob_elwaset.getValueAt(x, 0);
m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
              ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select eltrkebat.* , clients.name_client , clients_product.quantity  , elmndob.name_elmndob "
        + "     from eltrkebat"
                        + " left join clients_product  "
                        + "on eltrkebat.serial=clients_product.serial "
                        + " left join clients on clients.id_client=clients_product.id_client  "
                       
                        + " left join elmndob on eltrkebat.id_elmndob = elmndob.id_elmndob"
                        + " where eltrkebat.id_elmndob_elwaset=" + id_elmndob_elwaset
                        + " and eltrkebat.date between '" + month_year_day_start
                        + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");


                while (rs.next()) {
                   
                    String serial = rs.getString("serial");
                   String id = rs.getString("id");                
                    String id_elfne = rs.getString("id_elfne");
                    String id_elmndob = rs.getString("id_elmndob");
                    String mark = rs.getString("mark");

                    
                    String name_client 
                 = rs.getString("name_client");
                   
                  
                    String quantity =  rs.getString("quantity");
                    
                    if (id_elmndob==null) {
                        counter_m_w++;
                    } else {
                        counter_m_w_m++;
                    }
                  
                    String name_elmndob =
                    rs.getString("name_elmndob");
                    

                    model_operations_elmndob_elwset.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial, name_client, quantity, id_elfne, id_elmndob, name_elmndob, id_elmndob_elwaset, mark , "?????"});
                }
                jLabel_mndob_elwaset_m_w.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m_w));
                jLabel_mndob_elwaset_m_w_m.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m_w_m));
                
                //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
                   counter_m_w = 0;
                   counter_m_w_m = 0;  
              m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();     
                ResultSet rs_siana_gdeda = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select siana_gdeda_archive.* , clients.name_client , clients_product.quantity  , elmndob.name_elmndob "
        + "     from siana_gdeda_archive"
                        + " left join clients_product  "
                        + "on siana_gdeda_archive.serial=clients_product.serial "
                        + " left join clients on clients_product.id_client=clients.id_client  "
                       
                        + " left join elmndob on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob = elmndob.id_elmndob"
                        + " where siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob_elwaset=" + id_elmndob_elwaset
                        + " and siana_gdeda_archive.date between '" + month_year_day_start
                        + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");


                while (rs_siana_gdeda.next()) {
                  
                    String serial = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("serial");
                       String id = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id");
                 
                    String id_elfne = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id_elfne");
                    String id_elmndob = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("id_elmndob");
                    String mark = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("mark");

                    
                    String name_client 
                 = rs_siana_gdeda.getString("name_client");
                   
                  
                    String quantity =  rs_siana_gdeda.getString("quantity");
                    
                    if (id_elmndob==null) {
                        counter_m_w++;
                    } else {
                        counter_m_w_m++;
                    }
                  
                    String name_elmndob =
                    rs_siana_gdeda.getString("name_elmndob");
                    

                    model_operations_elmndob_elwset.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial, name_client,  quantity, id_elfne, id_elmndob, name_elmndob, id_elmndob_elwaset, mark,"????? ?????"});
                }
               
                jLabel_mndob_elwaset_m_w1.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m_w));
                jLabel_mndob_elwaset_m_w_m1.setText(String.valueOf(counter_m_w_m));

//////////////////////////////////////////////// canceled  report /////////////////////////////////////////////
                 int counter_canceled_trkeb = 0;
                 int counter_canceled_siana_gdeda= 0;
        model_elmndob_elwaset_canceled.setRowCount(0);
                m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
  ResultSet rs_canceld = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select canceled_table.*    , elmndob.name_elmndob "
        + "     from canceled_table"
                        
                        + " left join elmndob on canceled_table.id_elmndob = elmndob.id_elmndob"
                        + " where canceled_table.id_elmndob_elwaset=" + id_elmndob_elwaset
                        + " and canceled_table.date between '" + month_year_day_start
                        + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");

                while (rs_canceld.next()) {

                if (rs_canceld.getString(9).equals("?????"))  counter_canceled_trkeb++ ;
                    else if (rs_canceld.getString(9).equals("????? ?????")) counter_canceled_siana_gdeda++ ;
                   
                  model_elmndob_elwaset_canceled.addRow(new Object[]
                    {rs_canceld.getString(1),rs_canceld.getString(2),rs_canceld.getString(3),rs_canceld.getString(4),
                  rs_canceld.getString(5),rs_canceld.getString(6),rs_canceld.getString(9),rs_canceld.getString(7),rs_canceld.getString(10),rs_canceld.getString(8)});
                }

           jLabel_mndob_elwaset_trkeb_rejected.setText(String.valueOf(counter_canceled_trkeb));
           jLabel_mndob_elwaset_trkeb_rejected1.setText(String.valueOf(counter_canceled_siana_gdeda));
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
              Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        } 

    }

    private void formWindowClosing(java.awt.event.WindowEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_formWindowClosing

            m.save();
        }
        
    }//GEN-LAST:event_formWindowClosing
    void comp() {
      
        if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 1) {
            jTextField_st.setVisible(false);
            jTextField_en.setVisible(false);

            jLabel_st.setVisible(false);
            jLabel_en.setVisible(false);

            jLabel_n.setText("??? ??????");
            jLabel_n.setVisible(true);
            jTextField_n_p.setVisible(true);
jComboBox_elfne_clients_trport.setVisible(false);

        } else if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex() == 0) {
            jTextField_st.setVisible(false);
            jTextField_en.setVisible(false);

            jLabel_st.setVisible(false);
            jLabel_en.setVisible(false);

            jLabel_n.setText("??? ??????");
            jLabel_n.setVisible(true);

            jLabel_en.setVisible(false);

         }
