    private void jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE13KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE13KeyReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:
        String key = jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE1.getText();
        model_elfne_Elmo7sl.setRowCount(0);

        ResultSet rs = null;
        try {
            rs = m.ob.search_elmo7sl(key);
            while (rs.next()) {
                String id_elfne = String.valueOf(rs.getString(1));

                String name_elfne = rs.getString(2);

                String phone = String.valueOf(rs.getString(3));
                String places = rs.getString(4);
                model_elfne_Elmo7sl.addRow(new Object[]{id_elfne, name_elfne, phone, places});

            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_name_elfne_ELFNE13KeyReleased

    private void jTable_elfne_ELFNE1MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elfne_ELFNE1MouseReleased



        int counter = 0;


        String month_year_day_start = ((JTextField) jTextField_month_ELFNE1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();

        String month_year_day_end = ((JTextField) jTextField_year_ELFNE2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        int counter_places = 0;
        int x = jTable_elfne_ELFNE1.getSelectedRow();
        //   String month = jTextField_month_ELFNE.getText();
       
            if (x != -1 && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_end) == true && m.ob.check_time(month_year_day_start) == true) {
                model_operations_Elmo7sl.setRowCount(0);

                //  String time = m.ob.time_now();

                String id_elfne = (String) model_elfne_Elmo7sl.getValueAt(x, 0);
                try {
                    ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select* from el2st where id_elmo7sl=" + id_elfne + " and date between '" + month_year_day_start + "' and '" + month_year_day_end + "'");
                    

                    while (rs.next()) {

                        counter++;

                        String serial = rs.getString("serial");
                        String id = rs.getString("id");                       
                        String el2st = rs.getString("price");
                        String eltok3 = rs.getString("eltok3");
                        String date = rs.getString("date");

                        model_operations_Elmo7sl.addRow(new Object[]{id,serial, el2st, eltok3, date});


                    }



                    String places_elfne = String.valueOf(model_elfne_Elmo7sl.getValueAt(x, 3));
                    String Real_places_elfne="'";
                String curr="";
                for (int i=0 ; i<places_elfne.length() ; i++)
                {
                    if(places_elfne.charAt(i)=='-')
                    {
                        Real_places_elfne+=curr+"','";
                        curr="";
                    }else
                    {
                        curr+=places_elfne.charAt(i);
                    }
                }
                Real_places_elfne+=curr+"'";
                    m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                    ResultSet rs_places = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery(

                    "select (select count(*) from clients_product where date_el2st between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+"  "
                            + "and region in (select region from countries where country  in  ("+Real_places_elfne+") ) ) "
                    + "+"+"(select count(*) from el2st s left join clients_product cs on  s.serial=cs.serial "
                            + "  where date between "+"'"+month_year_day_start+"' and '"+month_year_day_end+"'"+" and cs."
                            + "region in (select region from countries where country  in  ("+Real_places_elfne+") ) ) as sum"
 
                    
                    );
                   
                    if (rs_places.next())
                    {
                        counter_places=rs_places.getInt(1);
                    }
                    




                } catch (SQLException ex) {
                    Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                }


                jLabel_TOTAL_Done_el2st.setText(String.valueOf(counter));
                jLabel_TOTAL_operation_el2st.setText(String.valueOf(counter_places));




            }
       

    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_elfne_ELFNE1MouseReleased

    private void jTextField1KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField1KeyReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:
  
        jComboBox_users.showPopup();
        if (jComboBox_users.getSelectedIndex()!=-1)
        { if (evt.getKeyCode() == 127) {

            jComboBox_users.removeItemAt(jComboBox_users.getSelectedIndex());
            
            java.io.File f = new java.io.File(directory,"CUSTOMER_SERVICES_USERS.txt");
            if (f.exists()) {


                PrintWriter w;
                try {
                    w = new PrintWriter(f);

                    for (int i = 0; i < jComboBox_users.getItemCount(); i++) {
                        w.println(jComboBox_users.getItemAt(i));
                    }
                    w.close();

                } catch (FileNotFoundException ex) {
                    Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                }



            }
        }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField1KeyReleased

void seach_Region_report()
{
     model_elkta3_info.setRowCount(0);
        String key=jTextField6.getText();
        for (int i=0 ; i<regions_rep.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (regions_rep.get(i).startsWith(key))
            {
                model_elkta3_info.addRow(new Object[]{regions_rep.get(i)});
            }
        }
        rep2();
}

    private void jTable_hintsKeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_hintsKeyReleased
            int x=jTable_hints.getSelectedRow();
   if (x!=-1)
   {
        if (evt.getKeyCode()==10)
      {
          if (jTable_hints.getSelectedColumn()==1)
          {
           
            try {
                m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update hints set hints='"+model_hints.getValueAt(x, 1) 
                        +"' "
                        +"where id="+String.valueOf(model_hints.getValueAt(x, 0)));
                JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null,"????? ?????");
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
           }
          else  if (jTable_hints.getSelectedColumn()==2)
          {
              try {
                m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update hints set "
                        +" date='"+model_hints.getValueAt(x, 2)+"' "
                        +"where id="+String.valueOf(model_hints.getValueAt(x, 0)));
                JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null,"????? ?????");
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
          }
      }
   }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_hintsKeyReleased

    int arr_elsiana[] = {0, 0};
    double total_elsiana = 0;
    int arr_eltrkeb[] = {0, 0, 0};
    double total_eltrkeb = 0;
    int arr_siana_gdeda[] = {0, 0, 0};
    double total_siana_gdeda = 0;
    int arr_el3otl[] = {0, 0, 0};
    double total_el3otl = 0;
    int arr_el2st[] = {0, 0};
    double total_el2st = 0;
    void clear_varibles()
    {
    arr_elsiana[0]=0; arr_elsiana[1]=0;
    total_elsiana = 0;
    arr_eltrkeb[0]=0; arr_eltrkeb[1]=0; arr_eltrkeb[2]=0;
    total_eltrkeb = 0;
    arr_siana_gdeda[0]=0; arr_siana_gdeda[1]=0; arr_siana_gdeda[2]=0;
    total_siana_gdeda = 0;
    arr_el3otl[0]=0; arr_el3otl[1]=0; arr_el3otl[2]=0;
    total_el3otl = 0;
    arr_el2st[0]=0 ;arr_el2st[1]=0 ;
    total_el2st = 0;
    }
    private void jLabel42MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel42MouseReleased
        //   model_selling.setRowCount(0);
        try {
           clear_varibles();
            String text_selling = ((JTextField) jTextField_date_selling_start.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
            String text_selling2 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date_selling_end.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
           
            if (m.ob.check_time(text_selling)&&m.ob.check_time(text_selling2))
            {
                elsiana_list_Done.clear();elsiana_list_not_Done.clear();
                el3otl_list_not_Done.clear();el3otl_list_1.clear();el3otl_list_mark2.clear();
                eltrkebat_list_mark1.clear();eltrkebat_list_mark2.clear();eltrkebat_list_not_done.clear();
                siana_gdeda_list_mark1.clear();siana_gdeda_list_mark2.clear();siana_gdeda_list_not_done.clear();
                el2st_list_done.clear(); el2st_list_nor_done.clear();
              //  int c = 0; double price=0 ;
                model_clients_sianat.setRowCount(0);
                m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                ResultSet rs_siana_num = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select elsiana.* "
                    + " ,clients_product.region , clients.name_client , elfne.name_elfne"
                    + " from elsiana left join clients_product on elsiana.serial=clients_product.serial"
               
                    +" left join clients on clients_product.id_client=clients.id_client "
                    +" left join elfne on elsiana.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                    + "where elsiana.date between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'");

                while (rs_siana_num.next()) {
                    String serial = rs_siana_num.getString("serial");
                    String id = rs_siana_num.getString("id");
                  
                    String type_elsiana = rs_siana_num.getString("type_elsiana");
                    String date = rs_siana_num.getString("date");
                    String id_elfne = rs_siana_num.getString("id_elfne");
                    String region=rs_siana_num.getString("region");
                    String name_client=rs_siana_num.getString("name_client");
                    String name_elfne=rs_siana_num.getString("name_elfne");
                    Double price_operation=rs_siana_num.getDouble("price");
                    total_elsiana+=price_operation;
                    arr_elsiana[1]++;
                    elsiana_list_Done.add(new elsiana(serial,name_client, id, type_elsiana, date, id_elfne,name_elfne,region,price_operation));

                    model_clients_sianat.addRow(new Object[]{serial,name_client, id, type_elsiana, date, id_elfne,name_elfne,region,price_operation});

                }

                    + " or date2 " + "between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'"
                    + " or date3 " + "between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'"
                    + " or date5 " + "between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'"
                    + " or date6 " + "between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'"

                model_fatorh_eltrkeb.setRowCount(0);

                ResultSet rs_trkebat = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select eltrkebat.* , elfne.name_elfne , clients.name_client , elmndob.name_elmndob "
                    + " , elmndob_elwaset.name_elmndob_elwaset "
                    + " ,clients_product.region "
                    + " from eltrkebat left join clients_product on eltrkebat.serial=clients_product.serial"
                 
                  
                    +" left join clients on clients_product.id_client=clients.id_client "
                    +" left join elfne on eltrkebat.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                    +" left join elmndob on eltrkebat.id_elmndob=elmndob.id_elmndob "
                    +" left join elmndob_elwaset on eltrkebat.id_elmndob_elwaset=elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset "
                    + "where eltrkebat.date between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'");
                while (rs_trkebat.next()) {
                    String serial = rs_trkebat.getString("serial");
                    String id = rs_trkebat.getString("id");
                    String date_regist = rs_trkebat.getString("date_regist");
                     String dead_line = rs_trkebat.getString("dead_line");
                    String date = rs_trkebat.getString("date");
                    String id_elfne = rs_trkebat.getString("id_elfne");
                    String id_elmndob = rs_trkebat.getString("id_elmndob");
                    String mark = rs_trkebat.getString("mark");
                    String region = rs_trkebat.getString("region");
                    String name_client= rs_trkebat.getString("name_client");
                    String name_elfne= rs_trkebat.getString("name_elfne");
                    String name_elmndob= rs_trkebat.getString("name_elmndob");
                    String name_elmndob_elwaset= rs_trkebat.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset");
                    String id_elmndob_elwaset= rs_trkebat.getString("id_elmndob_elwaset");
                    Double price_operation=rs_trkebat.getDouble("price");

                    if (mark.equals("2")) {

                    } else {
                       arr_eltrkeb[1]++;
                        eltrkebat_list_mark1.add(new eltrkebat(serial,name_client, id,date_regist, dead_line,date, mark, id_elfne, name_elfne

                    ,id_elmndob,name_elmndob,id_elmndob_elwaset,name_elmndob_elwaset,region,price_operation});

        model_siana_gdeda.setRowCount(0);
        m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();

        ResultSet rs_siana_gdeada = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select siana_gdeda_archive.* , elfne.name_elfne , clients.name_client , elmndob.name_elmndob "
            + " , elmndob_elwaset.name_elmndob_elwaset "
            + " ,clients_product.region "
            + " from siana_gdeda_archive left join clients_product on siana_gdeda_archive.serial=clients_product.serial"
         
            +" left join clients on clients_product.id_client=clients.id_client "
            +" left join elfne on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
            +" left join elmndob on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob=elmndob.id_elmndob "
            +" left join elmndob_elwaset on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob_elwaset=elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset "
            + "where siana_gdeda_archive.date between '" + text_selling + "' and '" + text_selling2 + "'");
        while (rs_siana_gdeada.next()) {
            String serial = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("serial");
            String id = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("id");
            String date_regist = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("date_regist");
            String dead_line = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("dead_line");
             String date = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("date");
            String id_elfne = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("id_elfne");
            String id_elmndob = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("id_elmndob");
            String mark = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("mark");
            String region = rs_siana_gdeada.getString("region");
            String name_client= rs_siana_gdeada.getString("name_client");
            String name_elfne= rs_siana_gdeada.getString("name_elfne");
            String name_elmndob= rs_siana_gdeada.getString("name_elmndob");
            String name_elmndob_elwaset= rs_siana_gdeada.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset");
            String id_elmndob_elwaset= rs_siana_gdeada.getString("id_elmndob_elwaset");
            Double price_operation=rs_siana_gdeada.getDouble("price");
            String what_done= rs_siana_gdeada.getString("what_done");
            total_siana_gdeda+=price_operation;

            if (mark.equals("2")) {
                arr_siana_gdeda[2]++;

                siana_gdeda_list_mark2.add(new elsiana_gdeda(serial,name_client, id,date_regist, dead_line,date, mark, id_elfne, name_elfne,id_elmndob,name_elmndob,id_elmndob_elwaset,name_elmndob_elwaset,region ,price_operation,what_done));

            } else {
               arr_siana_gdeda[1]++;
                siana_gdeda_list_mark1.add(new elsiana_gdeda(serial,name_client, id,date_regist, dead_line,date, mark, id_elfne, name_elfne
                    ,id_elmndob,name_elmndob,id_elmndob_elwaset,name_elmndob_elwaset,region , price_operation ,what_done));
        }
        model_siana_gdeda.addRow(new Object[]{serial,name_client, id,date_regist, dead_line,date, mark, id_elfne, name_elfne
            ,id_elmndob,name_elmndob,id_elmndob_elwaset,name_elmndob_elwaset,region,price_operation,what_done});

    }
//    jLabel_num_siana_gdeda_degree_1.setText(String.valueOf(tr_1));
//    jLabel_num_siana_gdeda_degree2.setText(String.valueOf(tr_2));
//    jLabel_price_siana_gdeda.setText(String.valueOf(price));

    m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();

    ResultSet rs_siana_gdeda_zero = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select region  from siana_gdeda where dead_line <= '" + text_selling2 + "'");
    while (rs_siana_gdeda_zero.next()) {

        String region = rs_siana_gdeda_zero.getString("region");
        arr_siana_gdeda[0]++;
        siana_gdeda_list_not_done.add(region);
        }
      //  jLabel_num_siana_gdeda_degree_0.setText(String.valueOf(tr_0));

        r.make_query();
        r.jPanel_compamy_reports.setVisible(true);
        r.setVisible(true);

        }

        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }

    private void jTextField7KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField7KeyReleased
        model_siana_gdeda.setRowCount(0);
        for (int i=0 ; i<siana_gdeda_list_mark2.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField7.getText()))
            {
                model_siana_gdeda.addRow(new Object[]{siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).serial,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).name_client,
                    siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).id,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).date_regist,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).dead_line,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).date, siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).mark,
                    siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).id_elfne,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).name_elfne
                    , siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).id_elmndob,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).name_elmndonb
                    ,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).id_elmndob_elwaset,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).name_elmndob_elwaset
                    ,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).region,siana_gdeda_list_mark2.get(i).price});
        }
        }
        for (int i=0 ; i<siana_gdeda_list_mark1.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField7.getText()))
            {
                model_siana_gdeda.addRow(new Object[]{siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).serial, siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).name_client,
                    siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).id, siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).date_regist,siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).dead_line,siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).date, siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).mark,
                    siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).id_elfne, siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).name_elfne
                    , siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).id_elmndob, siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).name_elmndonb
                    , siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).id_elmndob_elwaset, siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).name_elmndob_elwaset
                    ,siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).region,siana_gdeda_list_mark1.get(i).price});
        }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField7KeyReleased

            {

                     el2st_list_done.get(i).el2st,
                    el2st_list_done.get(i).eltok3, el2st_list_done.get(i).date,

        }
        }

    private void jTextField4KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField4KeyReleased
        model_fatorh_eltrkeb.setRowCount(0);
        for (int i=0 ; i<eltrkebat_list_mark2.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField4.getText()))
            {
                model_fatorh_eltrkeb.addRow(new Object[]{eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).serial,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).name_client,
                    eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).id,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).date_regist,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).dead_line,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).date, eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).mark,
                    eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).id_elfne,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).name_elfne
                    , eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).id_elmndob,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).name_elmndonb
                    ,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).id_elmndob_elwaset,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).name_elmndob_elwaset
                    ,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).region,eltrkebat_list_mark2.get(i).price});
        }
        }
        for (int i=0 ; i<eltrkebat_list_mark1.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField4.getText()))
            {
                model_fatorh_eltrkeb.addRow(new Object[]{eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).serial, eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).name_client,
                    eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).id, eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).date_regist,eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).dead_line,eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).date, eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).mark,
                    eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).id_elfne, eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).name_elfne
                    , eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).id_elmndob, eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).name_elmndonb
                    , eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).id_elmndob_elwaset, eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).name_elmndob_elwaset
                    ,eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).region,eltrkebat_list_mark1.get(i).price});
        }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField4KeyReleased

    private void jTextField3KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField3KeyReleased
        model_clients_el3otl.setRowCount(0);
        for (int i=0 ; i<el3otl_list_mark2.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField3.getText()))
            {
                model_clients_el3otl.addRow(new Object[]{el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).serial,el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).name_client, el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).id,
                     el3otl_list_mark2.get(i)
                    .mark, el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).type_el3otl, el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).date,
                    el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).id_elfne,el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).name_elfne,el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).region,el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).date_regist
                        ,el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).date_dead_line,el3otl_list_mark2.get(i).price});
        }
        }
        for (int i=0 ; i<el3otl_list_1.size() ; i++)
        {
            if (el3otl_list_1.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField3.getText()))
            {
                model_clients_el3otl.addRow(new Object[]{el3otl_list_1.get(i).serial,el3otl_list_1.get(i).name_client, el3otl_list_1.get(i).id,
                     el3otl_list_1.get(i)
                    .mark, el3otl_list_1.get(i).type_el3otl, el3otl_list_1.get(i).date,
                    el3otl_list_1.get(i).id_elfne,el3otl_list_1.get(i).name_elfne ,el3otl_list_1.get(i).region,el3otl_list_1.get(i).date_regist,el3otl_list_1.get(i).date_dead_line,el3otl_list_1.get(i).price});
        }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField3KeyReleased

    private void jTextField2KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField2KeyReleased
        model_clients_sianat.setRowCount(0);

        {

            if(elsiana_list_Done.get(i).name_client.contains(jTextField2.getText()))
            {
                model_clients_sianat.addRow(new Object[]{elsiana_list_Done.get(i).serial, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).name_client,elsiana_list_Done.get(i).id,
                    
                 elsiana_list_Done.get(i).type_siana, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).date, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).id_elfne,elsiana_list_Done.get(i).name_elfne,
                    elsiana_list_Done.get(i).region, elsiana_list_Done.get(i).price});
        }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField2KeyReleased

    private void jTable_elkta3_info1MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elkta3_info1MouseReleased
        try {
            int x = jTable_elkta3_info1.getSelectedRow();
            // TODO add your handling code here:

            if (x != -1) {
                model_elkta3_info.setRowCount(0);
                String country = String.valueOf(model_elkta3_info_country.getValueAt(x, 0));
                m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                ResultSet rs_regions = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select region from countries where country= '"
                    + country + "'");
                while (rs_regions.next()) {
                    model_elkta3_info.addRow(new Object[]{rs_regions.getString(1)});
                }
            }
            rep2();
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_elkta3_info1MouseReleased

    private void jTextField_elkta3KeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_elkta3KeyReleased
        // TODO add your handling code here:
        try {
            model_elkta3.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select * from elkta3 where name_elkta3 like '" + jTextField_elkta3.getText() + "%'");
            while (rs.next()) {
                model_elkta3.addRow(new Object[]{
                    rs.getString("id_elkta3"),
                    rs.getString("name_elkta3"),
                    rs.getString("date_construct"),
                    rs.getString("name_manager")
                });
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_elkta3KeyReleased

    private void jTable_elkta3_infoMouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_elkta3_infoMouseReleased
        String x=(String)model_elkta3_info.getValueAt(jTable_elkta3_info.getSelectedRow(), 0);
        model_elkta3_info.setRowCount(0);
        model_elkta3_info.addRow(new Object[]{x});
        rep2();
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_elkta3_infoMouseReleased

    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_main_elkta3MouseReleased

    private void jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana18MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana18MouseReleased
   
       
        if (opened!=jPanel_co_main && opened.getHeight()>=380)
    {
        m.animation(opened, 380);
        m.animation(jPanel_co_main, 380);
        opened=jPanel_co_main;  
        
        m.animate_separator_y(jPanel27,210);
         jPanel_percentages.setVisible(false); System.out.println(opened.getHeight());
    }
    
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana18MouseReleased

    private void jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana48MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana48MouseReleased
     
        if (opened!=jPanel_co_elsiana&& opened.getHeight()>=380)
    {
        m.animation(opened, 380);
        m.animation(jPanel_co_elsiana, 380);
        opened=jPanel_co_elsiana;  
        
         m.animate_separator_y(jPanel27,270);
    
      jPanel_percentages.setVisible(true);   System.out.println(opened.getHeight());
      
      jLabel_c_rep_2.setText("???????? ??????");
      jLabel_c_rep_1.setVisible(false);
      jLabel_c_rep_0.setText("???????? ????? ????");
      jLabel_c_rep_total.setText("?????? ????????");
      
      jLabel_c_rep_n2.setText(String.valueOf(arr_elsiana[1]));
      jLabel_c_rep_n1.setVisible(false);
      jLabel_c_rep_n0.setText(String.valueOf(arr_elsiana[0]));
      jLabel_c_rep_ntotal.setText(String.valueOf(total_elsiana));
      
     int p2=0;
     int p0=0;
    if (arr_elsiana[0]+arr_elsiana[1]!=0) 
    { p2=(arr_elsiana[1]*100)/(arr_elsiana[1]+arr_elsiana[0]);
      p0=(arr_elsiana[0]*100)/(arr_elsiana[1]+arr_elsiana[0]);
    }
   
      jLabel_c_rep_p1.setVisible(false);
      jLabel_c_rep_p2.setText(String.valueOf(p2)+"%");
      jLabel_c_rep_p0.setText(String.valueOf(p0)+"%");
      
      set_panel_persentage(jPanel_p2_f, (5*p2));
      set_panel_persentage(jPanel_p0_f, (5*p0));
      jPanel_p1_b.setVisible(false);
      jPanel_p1_f.setVisible(false);
    } 
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana48MouseReleased

    private void jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana22MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana22MouseReleased
          if (opened!=jPanel_co_el3otl  && opened.getHeight()>=380)

        jLabel_c_rep_1.setVisible(true);
        jPanel_percentages.setVisible(true);
        jLabel_c_rep_p1.setVisible(true);
        jPanel_p1_b.setVisible(true);
        jPanel_p1_f.setVisible(true);
      
      jLabel_c_rep_2.setText("??????? ????2");
      jLabel_c_rep_1.setText("??????? ????1");
      jLabel_c_rep_0.setText("??????? ????? ????");
      jLabel_c_rep_total.setText("?????? ???????");

      jLabel_c_rep_n1.setText(String.valueOf(arr_el3otl[1]));
      jLabel_c_rep_n0.setText(String.valueOf(arr_el3otl[0]));
      jLabel_c_rep_ntotal.setText(String.valueOf(total_el3otl));
      
     int p2=0;
     int p1=0 ;
     int p0=0;
    if (arr_el3otl[0]+arr_el3otl[1]+arr_el3otl[2]!=0) 
    { p2=(arr_el3otl[2]*100)/(arr_el3otl[2]+arr_el3otl[1]+arr_el3otl[0]);
      p1=(arr_el3otl[1]*100)/(arr_el3otl[2]+arr_el3otl[1]+arr_el3otl[0]);
      p0=(arr_el3otl[0]*100)/(arr_el3otl[2]+arr_el3otl[1]+arr_el3otl[0]);
    }
   
      jLabel_c_rep_p2.setText(String.valueOf(p2)+"%");
      jLabel_c_rep_p1.setText(String.valueOf(p1)+"%");
      jLabel_c_rep_p0.setText(String.valueOf(p0)+"%");
      
      set_panel_persentage(jPanel_p2_f, (5*p2));
      set_panel_persentage(jPanel_p1_f, (5*p1));
      set_panel_persentage(jPanel_p0_f, (5*p0));
    }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel_id_el2st_elsiana22MouseReleased

            update.action_delete();
           }

        }
    
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel52MouseReleased

    private void jPanel10MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jPanel10MouseReleased
          String id_sec = jTextField_id_sec.getText();
        String name_sec = jTextField_name_sec.getText();
        String date = ((JTextField) jTextField_date_sec.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
        String manager = jTextField_manager_sec.getText();
        boolean flag_int_id = m.ob.check_int(id_sec);
        boolean flag_sec = true;
        if (flag_int_id == false) {
            jTextField_id_sec.setBackground(Color.pink);
        } else {
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.search_id_sec(id_sec);
            try {
                if (rs.next()) {
                    flag_sec = false;
                    jTextField_id_sec.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
        }
        boolean flag_date = true;
       
            flag_date = m.ob.check_time(date);
            if (flag_date == false) {
                jTextField_date_sec.setBackground(Color.pink);
            }
       
        if (flag_date == true && flag_int_id == true && flag_sec == true) {
            m.ob.insert_elkta3(id_sec, name_sec, date, manager);
            jTextField_id_sec.setText("");
            jTextField_name_sec.setText("");
            ((JTextField) jTextField_date_sec.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
            jTextField_manager_sec.setText("");
            jTextField_id_sec.setBackground(Color.white);
            jTextField_name_sec.setBackground(Color.white);
            jTextField_date_sec.setBackground(Color.white);
            jTextField_manager_sec.setBackground(Color.white);
        }

    }//GEN-LAST:event_jPanel10MouseReleased

    private void jLabel8MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel8MouseReleased
       if ( jTable_elkt3at.getSelectedRow()!=-1 &&jTable_all_regions.getSelectedRow()!=-1)
{
        String id_elkta3 = (String) model_elkta3_insert.getValueAt(jTable_elkt3at.getSelectedRow(), 0);
        String region = (String) model_all_regions.getValueAt(jTable_all_regions.getSelectedRow(), 0);
        m.ob.insert_elkta3_dependant(id_elkta3, region);
        model_all_regions.removeRow(jTable_all_regions.getSelectedRow());

        regions_loaded.remove(region);
        regions_elkta3.add(region);
        model_elkta3_regions.addRow(new Object[]{region});
}

    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel8MouseReleased

    private void jLabel6MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel6MouseReleased
       int x = jTable_region_elkta3.getSelectedRow();

        if (x != -1) {


            String region = (String) model_elkta3_regions.getValueAt(x, 0);
            try {
                m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("delete from elkta3_dependant where country='" + region + "'");
                model_elkta3_regions.removeRow(x);
                regions_elkta3.remove(region);

                model_all_regions.addRow(new Object[]{region});
                regions_loaded.add(region);
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }

        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel6MouseReleased

    private void jLabel13MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel13MouseReleased
    
        int i = jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        if (i != -1) {
            int ch = JOptionPane.showConfirmDialog(null, "are you sure to save ?");
            if (ch == 0) {
                try {
//                    m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("start TRANSACTION ");
//                    m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("savepoint up");
                    String region = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 2));

                    String rsed_5 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 32));
                    String rsed_6 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 33));
                    String rsed_7 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 34));
                    String home_num = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 40));
                    String street = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 41));
                    String country = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 42));

                    String id_product = "";
                    String date_buy = "";

                    String phone = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 3));
                    String hints = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 4));


                    String date1 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 9));
                    String date2 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 10));
                    String date3 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 11));
                    String date5 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 12));
                    String date6 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 13));
                    String date7 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 14));

                    id_client = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 0));
                    id_product = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 5));
                    date_buy = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 8));

                    String siana_2 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 24));

                    String siana_7 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 28));
                    String type_3otl = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 16));
                    String date_wrong = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 17));
                    String date_end = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 19));
                    String wrongs = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 16));
                    String nezam_eldf3 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 18));
                    String el2st_product = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 20));
                    String date_el2st = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 21));

                    String elb2e = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 22));
                    String quantity = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 7));
                    String siana_elb2e = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 35));
                    String clas = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 36));
                    String elmosthdaf = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 37));
                    String date_remake_class = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 38));
                    String num_month_remake_class = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 39));
                    String type_siana = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 15));
                   
                    m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update clients set name_client='" + name_client + "' , phone='" + phone + "' where id_client=" + id_client);

                  

                    m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update clients_product set quantity=" + quantity + " , date1='" + date1 + "' , date2='" + date2 + "', "
                            + "date3='" + date3 + "' , date5='" + date5 + "' , date6='" + date6 + "' , date7='" + date7 + "' , hints='" + hints + "',"
                            + "  nezam_eldf3=" + nezam_eldf3 + " , date_el2st='" + date_el2st + "' , elb2e=" + elb2e + ",rsed1=" + rsed_1 + " ,"
                            + "rsed2=" + rsed_2 + " , rsed3=" + rsed_3 + " , rsed5=" + rsed_5 + " ,rsed6=" + rsed_6 + " , rsed7=" + rsed_7 + " , class='" + clas + "'"
                            + " , total_elb2e_sian=" + siana_elb2e + " , siana_1=" + siana_1 + " , siana_2=" + siana_2 + " , siana_3=" + siana_3 + " ,"
                            + " siana_5=" + siana_5 + " , siana_6=" + siana_6 + " , siana_7=" + siana_7 + " , date_remake_class='" + date_remake_class + "' ,"
                            + " num_month_remake_class=" + num_month_remake_class + " , elmosthdaf=" + elmosthdaf + ", home_num=" + home_num + " , "
                            + "street='" + street + "' , region='" + region + "' where serial=" + String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 43))
                            );
                    int rt=get_client_from_back_table(String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 43)));
                        if (rt!=-1)
                        {
                                    for (int c=0 ; c<model_search_client.getColumnCount() ; c++)
                            {
                               m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, c), rt, c);
                            }
                        }
                   
                      JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "?? ?????");
              //      m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("commit");
                } catch (SQLException ex) {
                 
                      //  m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("rollback to up");
                        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "Wrong \n" + ex.getMessage());
                   
                }
            }
        }

    private void jPanel16MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jPanel16MouseReleased
    int x = jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        if (x != -1) {
            
            String date1 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
            String date2 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
            String date3 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date3.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
            String date5 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date5.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
            String date6 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date6.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();
            String date7 = ((JTextField) jTextField_date7.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText();


               boolean flag_continue=true;
             
                if (m.ob.check_time(date1) == false) {
                    jTextField_date1.setBackground(Color.pink);flag_continue=false;
                }
               
                if (m.ob.check_time(date2)== false) {
                    jTextField_date2.setBackground(Color.pink);flag_continue=true;
                }
              
                if ( m.ob.check_time(date3)== false) {
                    jTextField_date3.setBackground(Color.pink);flag_continue=true;
                }
              
                if (m.ob.check_time(date5)== false) {
                    jTextField_date5.setBackground(Color.pink);flag_continue=true;
                }
               
                if (m.ob.check_time(date6)== false) {
                    jTextField_date6.setBackground(Color.pink);flag_continue=true;
                }
             
                if (m.ob.check_time(date7)== false) {
                    jTextField_date7.setBackground(Color.pink);flag_continue=true;
                }

                if (flag_continue) {
                    try {
                        
//                        System.out.println("update clien"
//                                + "ts_product set date1='" + date1 + "' , date2='" + date2 + "' , date3='" + date3
//                                + "' , date5='" + date5 + "' ,date6='" + date6 + "' , date7='" + date7 + "' where id_client=" + id_client
//                                + " and id_product=" + id_product + " and date_buy='" + date_buy + "'");
                   if (!jCheckBox_addd_candels_period.isSelected())  
                     {m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update clien"
                                + "ts_product set date1='" + date1 + "' , date2='" + date2 + "' , date3='" + date3
                                + "' , date5='" + date5 + "' ,date6='" + date6 + "' , date7='" + date7 + "' where serial=" + String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43))
                                );
                     }
                     else
                     {
                         if (!date1.startsWith("0"))date1=m.ob.time_month(date1, Integer.parseInt((String)model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 23)));
                         if (!date2.startsWith("0"))date2=m.ob.time_month(date2, Integer.parseInt((String)model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 24)));
                         if (!date3.startsWith("0"))date3=m.ob.time_month(date3, Integer.parseInt((String)model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 25)));
                         if (!date5.startsWith("0"))date5=m.ob.time_month(date5, Integer.parseInt((String)model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 26)));
                         if (!date6.startsWith("0"))date6=m.ob.time_month(date6, Integer.parseInt((String)model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 27)));
                         if (!date7.startsWith("0"))date7=m.ob.time_month(date7, Integer.parseInt((String)model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 28)));
                         
                          m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update clien"
                                + "ts_product set date1='" + date1 + "' , date2='" + date2 + "' , date3='" + date3
                                + "' , date5='" + date5 + "' ,date6='" + date6 + "' , date7='" + date7 + "' where serial=" + String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43))
                                );
                     
                       
                     }
                        

                        model_search_client.setValueAt(date1, x, 9);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(date2, x, 10);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(date3, x, 11);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(date5, x, 12);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(date6, x, 13);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(date7, x, 14);
                        int rt=get_client_from_back_table( String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43)));
                        if (rt!=-1)
                        {
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(date1, rt, 9);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(date2, rt, 10);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(date3, rt, 11);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(date5, rt, 12);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(date6, rt, 13);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(date7, rt, 14);
                        }
                        
                        
                        ((JTextField) jTextField_date1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
                        ((JTextField) jTextField_date2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
                        ((JTextField) jTextField_date3.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
                        ((JTextField) jTextField_date5.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
                        ((JTextField) jTextField_date6.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
                        ((JTextField) jTextField_date7.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText("");
                        jTextField_date1.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_date2.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_date3.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_date5.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_date6.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_date7.setBackground(Color.white);



                      

                    } catch (SQLException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }
                }


           



        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jPanel16MouseReleased

    private void jPanel13MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jPanel13MouseReleased
         int x = jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        if (x != -1) {
            System.out.println(x);
          
            here:
            {
                String rsed1 = jTextField_rsed1.getText();
                String rsed2 = jTextField_rsed2.getText();
                String rsed3 = jTextField_rsed3.getText();
                String rsed5 = jTextField_rsed5.getText();
                String rsed6 = jTextField_rsed6.getText();
                String rsed7 = jTextField_rsed7.getText();


                String total_rsed_1 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 29));
                String total_rsed_2 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 30));
                String total_rsed_3 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 31));
                String total_rsed_5 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 32));
                String total_rsed_6 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 33));
                String total_rsed_7 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 34));


                boolean flag_rsed1 = m.ob.check_int(rsed1);
                if (flag_rsed1 == false) {
                    jTextField_rsed1.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }

                if (Double.parseDouble(rsed1) + Double.parseDouble(total_rsed_1) < 0) {
                    jTextField_rsed1.setBackground(Color.pink);
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "??? ?? ???? ???? ????? ????1 ?? ?????? ??????? ??? ????? :(");
                }

                boolean flag_rsed2 = m.ob.check_int(rsed2);
                if (flag_rsed2 == false) {
                    jTextField_rsed2.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }

                if (Double.parseDouble(rsed2) + Double.parseDouble(total_rsed_2) < 0) {
                    jTextField_rsed2.setBackground(Color.pink);
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "??? ?? ???? ???? ????? ????2 ?? ?????? ??????? ??? ????? :(");
                }
                boolean flag_rsed3 = m.ob.check_int(rsed3);
                if (flag_rsed3 == false) {
                    jTextField_rsed3.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }

                if (Double.parseDouble(rsed3) + Double.parseDouble(total_rsed_3) < 0) {
                    jTextField_rsed3.setBackground(Color.pink);
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "??? ?? ???? ???? ????? ????3 ?? ?????? ??????? ??? ????? :(");
                }
                boolean flag_rsed5 = m.ob.check_int(rsed5);
                if (flag_rsed5 == false) {
                    jTextField_rsed5.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }

                if (Double.parseDouble(rsed5) + Double.parseDouble(total_rsed_5) < 0) {
                    jTextField_rsed5.setBackground(Color.pink);
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "??? ?? ???? ???? ????? ????5 ?? ?????? ??????? ??? ????? :(");
                }
                boolean flag_rsed6 = m.ob.check_int(rsed6);
                if (flag_rsed6 == false) {
                    jTextField_rsed6.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }

                if (Double.parseDouble(rsed6) + Double.parseDouble(total_rsed_6) < 0) {
                    jTextField_rsed6.setBackground(Color.pink);
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "??? ?? ???? ???? ????? ????6 ?? ?????? ??????? ??? ????? :(");
                }
                boolean flag_rsed7 = m.ob.check_int(rsed7);
                if (flag_rsed7 == false) {
                    jTextField_rsed7.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }

                if (Double.parseDouble(rsed7) + Double.parseDouble(total_rsed_7) < 0) {
                    jTextField_rsed7.setBackground(Color.pink);
                    JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "??? ?? ???? ???? ????? ????7 ?? ?????? ??????? ??? ????? :(");
                }

                System.out.println(flag_rsed1 + " " + flag_rsed2 + " " + flag_rsed3 + " " + flag_rsed5 + " " + flag_rsed6 + " " + flag_rsed7);

                if (flag_rsed1 == true && flag_rsed2 == true && flag_rsed3 == true && flag_rsed5 == true && flag_rsed6 == true && flag_rsed7 == true) {
                    try {
                      
                        m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update clients_product set rsed1=" + String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed1) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_1))
                                + " , rsed2=" + String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed2) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_2))
                                + " , rsed3=" + String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed3) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_3))
                                + " , rsed5=" + String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed5) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_5))
                                + " , rsed6=" + String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed6) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_6))
                                + " , rsed7=" + String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed7) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_7))
                                + " where serial=" + String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43)) );
                        
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed1) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_1)), x, 29);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed2) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_2)), x, 30);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed3) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_3)), x, 31);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed5) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_5)), x, 32);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed6) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_6)), x, 33);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed7) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_7)), x, 34);
                        int rt=get_client_from_back_table(String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43)));
                        if (rt!=-1)
                        {
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed1) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_1)), rt, 29);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed2) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_2)), rt, 30);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed3) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_3)), rt, 31);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed5) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_5)), rt, 32);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed6) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_6)), rt, 33);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(rsed7) + Integer.parseInt(total_rsed_7)), rt, 34);
                        }
               //          m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
//            ResultSet rs =  m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("SHOW TABLE STATUS WHERE `Name` = 'history_rsed'");
//            rs.next();
//            String nextid = rs.getString("Auto_increment");
           // System.out.println("next"+nextid);
//                        System.out.println("insert into history_rsed values (" + id_client + " , " + id_product
//                                + " , '" + date_buy + "' , " + rsed1 + " , " + rsed2 + " , " + rsed3 + " , " + rsed5 + " , " + rsed6 + " , " + rsed7 + " , '" + m.ob.time_now() + "'");
                        m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("insert into history_rsed values ("+"default"+ ","+ String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43))
                                + " , " + rsed1 + " , " + rsed2 + " , " + rsed3 + " , " + rsed5 + " , " + rsed6 + " , " + rsed7 + " , '" + m.ob.time_now() + "')");


                        jTextField_rsed1.setText("");
                        jTextField_rsed2.setText("");
                        jTextField_rsed3.setText("");
                        jTextField_rsed5.setText("");
                        jTextField_rsed6.setText("");
                        jTextField_rsed7.setText("");

                        jTextField_rsed1.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_rsed2.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_rsed3.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_rsed5.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_rsed6.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_rsed7.setBackground(Color.white);



                    } catch (SQLException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }


                }


            }

        }

    private void jPanel14MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jPanel14MouseReleased
        int x = jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        if (x != -1) {
            System.out.println(x);
           
            here:
            {
                String time1 = jTextField_time1.getText();
                String time2 = jTextField_time2.getText();
                String time3 = jTextField_time3.getText();
                String time5 = jTextField_time5.getText();
                String time6 = jTextField_time6.getText();
                String time7 = jTextField_time7.getText();





                boolean flag_time1 = m.ob.check_int(time1);
                if (flag_time1 == false) {
                    jTextField_time1.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }


                boolean flag_time2 = m.ob.check_int(time2);
                if (flag_time2 == false) {
                    jTextField_time2.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }


                boolean flag_time3 = m.ob.check_int(time3);
                if (flag_time3 == false) {
                    jTextField_time3.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }


                boolean flag_time5 = m.ob.check_int(time5);
                if (flag_time5 == false) {
                    jTextField_time5.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }


                boolean flag_time6 = m.ob.check_int(time6);
                if (flag_time6 == false) {
                    jTextField_time6.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }


                boolean flag_time7 = m.ob.check_int(time7);
                if (flag_time7 == false) {
                    jTextField_time7.setBackground(Color.pink);
                }





                if (flag_time1 == true && flag_time2 == true && flag_time3 == true && flag_time5 == true && flag_time6 == true && flag_time7 == true) {
                    try {
                      
                        m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update clients_product set siana_1=" + time1
                                + " , siana_2=" + time2
                                + " , siana_3=" + time3
                                + " , siana_5=" + time5
                                + " , siana_6=" + time6
                                + " , siana_7=" + time7
                                + " where serial=" + String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43)) );

                        model_search_client.setValueAt(time1, x, 23);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(time2, x, 24);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(time3, x, 25);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(time5, x, 26);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(time6, x, 27);
                        model_search_client.setValueAt(time7, x, 28);
                        int tr=get_client_from_back_table(String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43)));
                        if (tr!=0)
                        {
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(time1, tr, 23);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(time2, tr, 24);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(time3, tr, 25);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(time5, tr, 26);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(time6, tr, 27);
                            m.model_siana_help.setValueAt(time7, tr, 28);
                        }
                        jTextField_time1.setText("");
                        jTextField_time2.setText("");
                        jTextField_time3.setText("");
                        jTextField_time5.setText("");
                        jTextField_time6.setText("");
                        jTextField_time7.setText("");

                        jTextField_time1.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_time2.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_time3.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_time5.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_time6.setBackground(Color.white);
                        jTextField_time7.setBackground(Color.white);



                    } catch (SQLException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }


                }


            }

        }

    }//GEN-LAST:event_jPanel14MouseReleased

    private void jLabel67MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel67MouseReleased
       jScrollPane5.setSize(jScrollPane5.getWidth(),250);
        if (jPanel11.getHeight()>0)
       {
            jScrollPane5.setSize(jScrollPane5.getWidth(),430);
            jScrollPane38.setSize(jScrollPane38.getWidth(),400);
            jPanel8.setSize(jPanel8.getWidth(),400);
            jLabel67.setIcon(new javax.swing.ImageIcon(getClass().getResource("/ph/icons/double-arrow-down-32.png"))); 
            jLabel67.setToolTipText("????? ????? ?????????");
             jTable_siana.setSize(jTable_siana.getWidth(),400);
            
       }
        else
        {
               jScrollPane5.setSize(jScrollPane5.getWidth(),210);
               
                jScrollPane38.setSize(jScrollPane38.getWidth(),190);
                jTable_siana.setSize(jTable_siana.getWidth(),190);
                jPanel8.setSize(jPanel8.getWidth(),190);
                
             jLabel67.setIcon(new javax.swing.ImageIcon(getClass().getResource("/ph/icons/double-arrow-up-32.png"))); 
             jLabel67.setToolTipText("????? ????? ?????????");
        }
        m.animation(jPanel11, 190);
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel67MouseReleased

    private void jLabel68MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel68MouseReleased
        int i =jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        if (i!=-1)
        {
            String serial = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(i, 43));

            String text=jTextArea2.getText();
            String date=m.ob.time_now();

            try {
                m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
                ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("SHOW TABLE STATUS WHERE `Name` = 'hints'");
               String nextid="";
                if (rs.next()) 
               {   nextid = rs.getString("Auto_increment");
               }
               
//                System.out.println("next"+nextid);
//                System.out.println("insert into hints values ("+nextid+","+serial+",'"+text+"','"
//                    +date+"')");
                m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("insert into hints values ("+nextid+","+serial+",'"+text+"','"
                    +date+"')");
                model_hints.addRow(new Object[]{nextid,text,date});
                jTextArea2.setText("");
                
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "?? ??? ??????? :(");
                 JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null,ex.getMessage());
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel68MouseReleased

    private void jLabel69MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel69MouseReleased
       int x=jTable_hints.getSelectedRow();
        if (x!=-1)
        {
            try {
                m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("delete from hints where id="+String.valueOf(model_hints.getValueAt(x, 0)));
                model_hints.removeRow(x);
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(main.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel69MouseReleased

    private void jLabel63MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel63MouseReleased

       {
          m.animation(opened_cl_rep, 560);
           m.animation(jPanel_main_cl_rep, 560);
           opened_cl_rep=jPanel_main_cl_rep;
          
           m.animate_separator_y(jPanel2, 90);
           jPanel15.setVisible(false);
       }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel63MouseReleased

    private void jLabel70MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel70MouseReleased
         if (m.ob.check_time(((JTextField) jTextField_month_ELFNE1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText())
                &&m.ob.check_time(((JTextField) jTextField_year_ELFNE2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText())) {
            
        r.report_elmo7sl(((JTextField) jTextField_month_ELFNE1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText(), ((JTextField) jTextField_year_ELFNE2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText());
        r.homeCard.show(r.jPanel1, "card_elmo7sl");
        r.card_select = 3;
        r.jPanel_compamy_reports.setVisible(false);
        r.jPanel_elfne_reports.setVisible(true);
        r.setVisible(true);

      }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel70MouseReleased

    private void jLabel76MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel76MouseReleased
           if (m.ob.check_time(((JTextField) jTextField_month_ELFNE.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText())
                &&m.ob.check_time(((JTextField) jTextField_year_ELFNE1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText())) {
            
        r.report_elfne(((JTextField) jTextField_month_ELFNE.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText(), ((JTextField) jTextField_year_ELFNE1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).getText());
        r.homeCard.show(r.jPanel1, "card_elfne");
        r.card_select = 0;
        r.jPanel_compamy_reports.setVisible(false);
        r.jPanel_elfne_reports.setVisible(true);
        r.setVisible(true);
        

      }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel76MouseReleased

    private void jLabel74MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel74MouseReleased
        int ch=JOptionPane.showConfirmDialog(null, "??????? ???? ??? ? ??????? ???? ?? ?");
        if (ch==0)
        {
        print_object.set_table(jTable_operations_ELMNDOB);
        print_object.Load();
        jDialog_print.setVisible(true);
        }else if (ch==1)
        {
        try {
            m.ob.write_excel(jTable_operations_ELMNDOB);
        } catch (IOException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        } catch (WriteException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel74MouseReleased

    private void jLabel20MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel20MouseReleased

        if (model_update.getRowCount()!=0)
        {   String confirm_text=  JOptionPane.showInputDialog(null, "??? ??? ???? ???? ???? ???? ?????? ?? ?????? ??? ???? ?") ;
            if (confirm_text!=null)      
             {
                 if (confirm_text.equals("??? ????"))
                 {
                     update.delete_all();
                 }
                 
             }
        } 
        else
        {
            JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "???? ?????? ?????? ??? ?? ???? ?????");
        }
       
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel20MouseReleased

    private void jLabel84MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel84MouseReleased
        int ch = JOptionPane.showConfirmDialog(null, "??????? ???? ??? ? ??????? ???? ?? ?");
        if (ch == 0) {
            print_object.set_table(jTable_clients_el23tal);
            print_object.Load();
            jDialog_print.setVisible(true);
        } else if (ch == 1) {
            try {
                m.ob.write_excel(jTable_clients_el23tal);
            } catch (IOException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            } catch (WriteException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel84MouseReleased

    private void jLabel87MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel87MouseReleased
        if (jTable_numbers.getSelectedRow()!=-1)
        { 
            try {
                m.ob.stmt.executeUpdate("update contacts set name='"+jLabel_name_numbers.getText()
                        +"' , phone='"+(String)model_numbers.getValueAt(jTable_numbers.getSelectedRow(),0)+"' where user_name='"+user_name+"'");
                JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "please press scan in your mobile");
            } catch (SQLException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel87MouseReleased

    private void jComboBox_class_clients_reportActionPerformed(java.awt.event.ActionEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jComboBox_class_clients_reportActionPerformed
        model_search_client.setRowCount(0);
           if (jComboBox_class_clients_report.getSelectedIndex()==0)
           {
               for (int i=0 ; i<m.model_siana_help.getRowCount() ; i++)
               {
                   add(i);
               }
           }
           else
           {
               String clas=(String)jComboBox_class_clients_report.getSelectedItem();
                for (int i=0 ; i<m.model_siana_help.getRowCount() ; i++)
               {
                  if (clas.equalsIgnoreCase((String) m.model_siana_help.getValueAt(i, 36))) add(i);
               }
           }
          jLabel_count.setText(String.valueOf(model_search_client.getRowCount()));
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jComboBox_class_clients_reportActionPerformed

    private void jLabel103MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel103MouseReleased
      if (jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()!=-1)
      {
            
          jTable_print.removeColumn(jTable_print.getColumnModel().getColumn(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()));
          model_print_columns.removeRow(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()); 
          jTable_print.repaint();
      }
      else
      {
          JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "???? ??? ????? ?? ???? :(");
      }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel103MouseReleased

    private void jLabel106MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel106MouseReleased
      if (m.ob.check_int(jTextField_header_font.getText())&&m.ob.check_int(jTextField_table_font.getText()))
      {
          if (jTextField_header_font.getText().length()<5&&jTextField_table_font.getText().length()<5)
          {
             
              jTable_print.setFont(m.font.deriveFont(Float.parseFloat(jTextField_table_font.getText()+"f")));
              jTable_print.getTableHeader().setFont(m.font.deriveFont(Float.parseFloat(jTextField_header_font.getText()+"f")));
           
          }
         
         
      }
     
      
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel106MouseReleased

    private void jLabel107MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel107MouseReleased
//        MessageFormat header=new MessageFormat(jLabel_print_name.getText()+"-"+String.valueOf(model_print.getRowCount()));
//        MessageFormat footer=new MessageFormat("page{1,number,integer}"+String.valueOf(model_print.getRowCount()));
//        try {
//           
//            boolean complete = jTable_print.print(JTable.PrintMode.FIT_WIDTH, header, footer);
//        } catch (PrinterException ex) {
//            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
//        }
        
        
//JTable jTable2 = new JTable();
//
try {
    PrinterJob job = PrinterJob.getPrinterJob();
MessageFormat[][] header = new MessageFormat[model_headers.getRowCount()][3];
for (int i=0 ; i<model_headers.getRowCount() ; i++)
{
    header[i][0]=new MessageFormat(String.valueOf(model_headers.getValueAt(i, 0)));
    header[i][1]=new MessageFormat(String.valueOf(model_headers.getValueAt(i, 1)));
    header[i][2]=new MessageFormat(String.valueOf(model_headers.getValueAt(i, 2)));
}
MessageFormat[][] footer = new MessageFormat[model_footers.getRowCount()+1][3];
    footer[0][0]=new MessageFormat("Page{0,number,integer} - "+String.valueOf(Integer.parseInt(String.valueOf(model_print.getRowCount()))));
    footer[0][1]=new MessageFormat("0");
    footer[0][2]=new MessageFormat("1"); 


for (int i=0 ; i<model_footers.getRowCount() ; i++)
{
    footer[i+1][0]=new MessageFormat(String.valueOf(model_footers.getValueAt(i, 0)));
    footer[i+1][1]=new MessageFormat(String.valueOf(model_footers.getValueAt(i, 1)));
    footer[i+1][2]=new MessageFormat(String.valueOf(model_footers.getValueAt(i, 2)));
}

job.setPrintable(new MyTablePrintable(jTable_print, PrintMode.FIT_WIDTH, header, footer));

if(job.printDialog())job.print();

} catch (PrinterException ex) {

}

    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel107MouseReleased

    private void jTable_print_columnsKeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTable_print_columnsKeyReleased
     if (evt.getKeyCode()==10){
      //  JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()+(String)model_print_columns.getValueAt(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow(), 1));
        jTable_print.getTableHeader() .getColumnModel().getColumn(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()).setHeaderValue(model_print_columns.getValueAt(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow(), 1));
        jTable_print.getTableHeader().repaint();
     }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTable_print_columnsKeyReleased

    private void jLabel115MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel115MouseReleased
       if (jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()!=0)
       {    
        if (jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()!=-1)
        {
           jTable_print.moveColumn(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow(), jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()-1);
           model_print_columns.moveRow(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow(),jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow() ,jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()-1);
          jTable_print_columns.setRowSelectionInterval(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()-1,jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()-1);
        }
        else
        {
            JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "?? ?????? ?? ????");
        }
       }
       else
       {
            JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "???? ???? ?????? ??? ?? ???????");
       }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel115MouseReleased

    private void jLabel114MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel114MouseReleased
         if (jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()!=model_print_columns.getRowCount()-1)
       {  
        if (jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()!=-1)
        {
           jTable_print.moveColumn(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow(), jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()+1);
             model_print_columns.moveRow(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow(),jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow() ,jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()+1);
        jTable_print_columns.setRowSelectionInterval(jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()+1,jTable_print_columns.getSelectedRow()+1);
        }
        else
        {
            JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "?? ?????? ?? ????");
        }
       }
       else
       {
            JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, "???? ???? ????????? ?? ???????");
       }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel114MouseReleased

    private void jTextField_key_table_namesKeyReleased(java.awt.event.KeyEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jTextField_key_table_namesKeyReleased
  model_db.setRowCount(0);
        for(int i=0 ; i<name_tables.size();i++)
    {
        if (name_tables.get(i).contains(jTextField_key_table_names.getText()))
        {
            model_db.addRow(new Object[]{name_tables.get(i)});
        }
    }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jTextField_key_table_namesKeyReleased

    private void jLabel113MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel113MouseReleased
        int ch = JOptionPane.showConfirmDialog(null, "??????? ???? ??? ? ??????? ???? ?? ?");
        if (ch == 0) {
            print_object.set_table(jTable_clients_siana);
            print_object.Load();
            jDialog_print.setVisible(true);
        } else if (ch == 1) {
       try {
                m.ob.write_excel(jTable_clients_siana);
            } catch (IOException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            } catch (WriteException ex) {
                Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
            }
        }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel113MouseReleased

    private void jLabel120MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel120MouseReleased
     if (print_object.validations_headers_footers(jTextField_name_hf.getText(), jTextField_level_hf.getText(), jTextField_positin_hf.getText()))
     {
         model_footers.addRow(new Object[]{jTextField_name_hf.getText(), jTextField_level_hf.getText(), jTextField_positin_hf.getText()});
          jTextField_name_hf.setBackground(Color.white); jTextField_positin_hf.setBackground(Color.white);   jTextField_level_hf.setBackground(Color.white);
     }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel120MouseReleased

    private void jLabel121MouseReleased(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jLabel121MouseReleased
         if (print_object.validations_headers_footers(jTextField_name_hf.getText(), jTextField_level_hf.getText(), jTextField_positin_hf.getText()))
     {
         model_headers.addRow(new Object[]{jTextField_name_hf.getText(), jTextField_level_hf.getText(), jTextField_positin_hf.getText()});
         jTextField_name_hf.setBackground(Color.white); jTextField_positin_hf.setBackground(Color.white);   jTextField_level_hf.setBackground(Color.white);
     }
    }//GEN-LAST:event_jLabel121MouseReleased

    private void jComboBox_elfne_clients_trportActionPerformed(java.awt.event.ActionEvent evt) {//GEN-FIRST:event_jComboBox_elfne_clients_trportActionPerformed
