    }//GEN-LAST:event_jComboBox_elfne_clients_trportActionPerformed
  
    void set_panel_persentage(final JPanel panel ,final  int persentage)
    {
 if (m.jCheckBox_animate.isSelected())
 {
        new Thread() {
            public void run() {
                if (panel.getWidth()<persentage)
                {
                while (panel.getWidth() <persentage) {
                    panel.setSize(panel.getWidth()+2, panel.getHeight());
                    try {
                        Thread.sleep(5);
                    } catch (InterruptedException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }
                   
                }
                }
                else
                {
                   while (panel.getWidth() >persentage) {
                    panel.setSize(panel.getWidth()-2, panel.getHeight());
                    try {
                        Thread.sleep(5);
                    } catch (InterruptedException ex) {
                        Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
                    }
                
                } 
                }
            }
        }.start();
 }
  panel.setSize(persentage, panel.getHeight());
    }
 void action_jtable() {
        int x = jTable_siana.getSelectedRow();
        if (x!=-1){
            
            if (jComboBox1.getSelectedIndex()==11)jLabel_n.setText(jTable_siana.getColumnName(jTable_siana.getSelectedColumn()));
        
      
        String serial = (String) model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 43);
        String date1 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 9));
        String date2 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 10));
        String date3 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 11));
        String date5 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 12));
        String date6 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 13));
        String date7 = String.valueOf(model_search_client.getValueAt(x, 14));
        ((JTextField) jTextField_date1.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText(date1);
        ((JTextField) jTextField_date2.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText(date2);
        ((JTextField) jTextField_date3.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText(date3);
        ((JTextField) jTextField_date5.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText(date5);
        ((JTextField) jTextField_date6.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText(date6);
        ((JTextField) jTextField_date7.getDateEditor().getUiComponent()).setText(date7);



        try {
            model_siana.setRowCount(0);
             m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
          
             
            ResultSet rs_siana = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select elsiana.* , elfne.name_elfne from elsiana "
                    +" left join elfne on elsiana.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                    + " where serial= " + serial   );
            while (rs_siana.next()) {
                String type_elsiana = rs_siana.getString("type_elsiana");
                String date = rs_siana.getString("date");
                model_siana.addRow(new Object[]{rs_siana.getString("id"), type_elsiana,rs_siana.getString("id_elfne"),
                    rs_siana.getString("name_elfne")
                        ,date , rs_siana.getDouble("price")});
             //   System.out.println(type_elsiana);
            }
            model_el3otl.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs_el3otl = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select el3otl.* , elfne.name_elfne from el3otl  "
                     +" left join elfne on el3otl.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                    + "where serial=" + serial );
            while (rs_el3otl.next()) {
                String type_el3otl = rs_el3otl.getString("type_el3otl");
                String date = rs_el3otl.getString("date");
                model_el3otl.addRow(new Object[]{rs_el3otl.getString("id"), type_el3otl,rs_el3otl.getString("id_elfne")
                        ,rs_el3otl.getString("name_elfne"), date,rs_el3otl.getDouble("price")});
            }



            model_el2rsdh.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs_el2rsdh = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select id , q_rsed1 , q_rsed2 , q_rsed3 , q_rsed5 , q_rsed6 , q_rsed7 ,date "
                    + "   from history_rsed where serial=" + serial );

            while (rs_el2rsdh.next()) {

                String rsed1 = rs_el2rsdh.getString("q_rsed1");
                String rsed2 = rs_el2rsdh.getString("q_rsed2");
                String rsed3 = rs_el2rsdh.getString("q_rsed3");
                String rsed5 = rs_el2rsdh.getString("q_rsed5");
                String rsed6 = rs_el2rsdh.getString("q_rsed6");
                String rsed7 = rs_el2rsdh.getString("q_rsed7");
                String date = rs_el2rsdh.getString("date");




                model_el2rsdh.addRow(new Object[]{rs_el2rsdh.getString("id"),rsed1, rsed2, rsed3, rsed5, rsed6, rsed7, date});
            }

            model_elb2e_siana.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs_elb2e_siana = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select id, price ,date "
                    + "   from history_siana_elb2e where serial=" + serial );

            while (rs_elb2e_siana.next()) {

                String price = rs_elb2e_siana.getString("price");
                String date = rs_elb2e_siana.getString("date");

                model_elb2e_siana.addRow(new Object[]{ rs_elb2e_siana.getString("id"),price, date});
            }

            model_el2st_client.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs_el2st_client = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select el2st.* , elmo7sl.name_elmo7sl from el2st "
                     +" left join elmo7sl on el2st.id_elmo7sl=elmo7sl.id_elmo7sl "
                    + " where serial=" + serial );

            double total = 0;
            while (rs_el2st_client.next()) {

                double E = rs_el2st_client.getDouble(3);
                total += E;

                model_el2st_client.addRow(new Object[]{rs_el2st_client.getString(1), E, rs_el2st_client.getString(4),
                            rs_el2st_client.getString(5), rs_el2st_client.getString(6),rs_el2st_client.getString(7)});
            }
         //   System.out.println(total);
            jLabel_el2st_client.setText(String.valueOf(total));

            
              model_class_client.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs_class_client = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select id , old_class , new_class , num_sianat ,date from client_class_history where serial=" + serial );
            while (rs_class_client.next()) {
              
                model_class_client.addRow(new Object[]{ rs_class_client.getString(1),rs_class_client.getString(2), 
                rs_class_client.getString(3),rs_class_client.getString(4),rs_class_client.getString(5)});
            }
            
             model_hints.setRowCount(0);
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select id , hints , date from hints " + " where serial =" + serial
                  );
            while (rs.next()) {
                 String id = rs.getString("id");
                String hints = rs.getString("hints");
                String date = rs.getString("date");
               model_hints.addRow(new Object[]{id ,hints, date});
            
            }
            
            
            
             m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs_trkeb = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select * from eltrkebat  " 
                    +" left join elfne on eltrkebat.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                     +" left join elmndob on eltrkebat.id_elmndob=elmndob.id_elmndob "
                     +" left join elmndob_elwaset on eltrkebat.id_elmndob_elwaset=elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset "
                    + " where eltrkebat.serial =" + serial
                  );
            here:
            {
            if (rs_trkeb.next()) {
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_id.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("id"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_type.setText("???? ????? ????");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_date_regist.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("date_regist"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_dead_line.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("dead_line"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_degree.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("mark"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elfne.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elfne"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elmndob.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elmndob"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elmndob_elwaset.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_price.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("price"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_date.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("date"));
                  jLabel128.setVisible(false);
                  jLabel_cl_rep_what_done_s.setVisible(false);
                 break here ;
            }
            ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
              
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
             rs_trkeb = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select * from siana_gdeda_archive  " 
                    +" left join elfne on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                     +" left join elmndob on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob=elmndob.id_elmndob "
                     +" left join elmndob_elwaset on siana_gdeda_archive.id_elmndob_elwaset=elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset "
                    + " where siana_gdeda_archive.serial =" + serial
                  );
              if (rs_trkeb.next()) {
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_id.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("id"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_type.setText("???? ????? ?????");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_date_regist.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("date_regist"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_dead_line.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("dead_line"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_degree.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("mark"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elfne.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elfne"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elmndob.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elmndob"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elmndob_elwaset.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_price.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("price"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_date.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("date"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_what_done_s.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("what_done"));
                   jLabel128.setVisible(true);
                  jLabel_cl_rep_what_done_s.setVisible(true);
                 break here ;
            }
              //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
             
              m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
             rs_trkeb = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select elfne.name_elfne , elmndob.name_elmndob , elmndob_elwaset.name_elmndob_elwaset from clients_product  " 
                    +" left join elfne on clients_product.id_elfne=elfne.id_elfne "
                     +" left join elmndob on clients_product.id_elmndob=elmndob.id_elmndob "
                     +" left join elmndob_elwaset on clients_product.id_elmndob_elwset=elmndob_elwaset.id_elmndob_elwaset "
                    + " where clients_product.serial =" + serial
                  );
              if (rs_trkeb.next()) {
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_id.setText("");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_type.setText("???? ????");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_date_regist.setText("");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_dead_line.setText("");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_degree.setText("");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elfne.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elfne"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elmndob.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elmndob"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_elmndob_elwaset.setText(rs_trkeb.getString("name_elmndob_elwaset"));
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_price.setText("");
                  jLabel_cl_rep_trkeb_date.setText("");
                   jLabel128.setVisible(false);
                  jLabel_cl_rep_what_done_s.setVisible(false);
                 break here ;
            }
            }
            
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
        }
    }

    void load_regions() {
        model_all_regions.setRowCount(0);
        regions_loaded.clear();
        try {
            m.ob.stmt = m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs = m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select distinct country from countries where country not in (select country from elkta3_dependant )");
            while (rs.next()) {
                String region = rs.getString("country");
                model_all_regions.addRow(new Object[]{region});
                regions_loaded.add(region);
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }

    }
void alarm_trkeb()
{
   
        try { 
            m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs=m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select count(*) from trkeb ");
            if (rs.next())
            { 
                int num= rs.getInt(1);
          
              
                    m.jLabel_installation_notify.setText(String.valueOf(num));
                    
                
               
               
           }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
}
void alarm_siana_gdeda()
{
    try { 
            m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs=m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select count(*) from siana_gdeda ");
            if (rs.next())
            {
            int num= rs.getInt(1);
            
                   m.jLabel_new_servising_notify.setText(String.valueOf(num));
                  
                   
            
            
           
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
}
void alarm_damage()
{
    try { 
            m.ob.stmt=m.ob.conn.createStatement();
            ResultSet rs=m.ob.stmt.executeQuery("select count(*) from wrongs ");
            if (rs.next())
            { int num= rs.getInt(1);
           
               m.jLabel_wrong_notify.setText(String.valueOf(num));
             
            
          
            }
        } catch (SQLException ex) {
            Logger.getLogger(hr.class.getName()).log(Level.SEVERE, null, ex);
        }
}
